hadiths[232]{hadithnumber,text}:
2263,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne kaha : maine Amr-bin-Yahyaa-bin-Ammaara se puchha to unhon-ne mujhey apne walid se khabar di, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : panch wasq se kam ( ghalley ya khajoor ( mein sadqa ( zakat ( nahi aur na panch se kam oonton mein sadqa hai aur na hi panch auqiya se kam ( chandi ( mein sadqa hai."
2264,Yahya-bin-Saeed ne Amr-bin-Yahyaa se uper zikr ki gaee sanad ke sath usi ki tarah bayan kiya.
2265,"ibne-Juraij ne kaha : mujhey Amr-bin-Yahyaa-bin-Ammaara ne apne walid Yahyaa-bin-Ammaara se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni hatheli se apni panchon ungliyon se ishara kya. padhi. phir (ibne-Juraij ne Sufiyan (bin Uena ki hadis ki tarah bayan kiya."
2266,"Umara-bin-Ghazziya ne Yahyaa-bin-Ammaara se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : panch wasq se kam ( khajoor ya ghalley ( mein sadqa nahi aur panch se kam oonton mein sadqa nahi aur panch auqiya se kam ( chandi ( mein sadqa nahi."
2267,"Wakee ne Sufiyan se, unhon-ne Ismail-bin-Umayya se, unhon-ne Muhammad-bin-Yahyaa-bin-hibbaan se, unhon-ne Yahyaa-bin-Ammaara se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : panch wasq se kam khajoor aur ghalley mein sadqa nahi hai."
2268,Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi ne Sufiyan se baqi bachi pichhli sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : na ghalley mein sadqa hai na khajoor mein yahan tak ke wo panch wasq tak pahunch jayen aur na panch se kam oonton mein sadqa hai aur na panch auqiya se kam ( chandi ( mein sadqa hai.
2269,yahyaa-bin-aadam ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan Sory ne Ismail-bin-Umayya se usi uper zikr ki gaee sanad ke sath ibne- Mehdi ki hadis ki tarah bayan kiya.
2270,"Abdur-Razzaq ne kaha : hamein Sory aur Mamar ne Ismail bin-Umayya se isi sanad ke sath , ibne- Mehdi aur yahyaa-bin-aadam ki hadis ki tarah bayan kiya, albatta unhon-ne  khajoor  ke bajaey samar ( phal ( kaha."
2271,Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se khabar di ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : panch auqiya se kam chandi mein sadqa nahi aur na panch oonton se kam mein sadqa hai aur na hi panch wasq se kam khajooron mein sadqa hai.
2272,Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna aap ne farmaya : jis ( kheti ( ko dariya ka pani ya barish sairaab karey unmein ushr ( daswaan hissey ( hai aur jis ko oont ( wghaira kisi janwar ke zariey ( se sairaab kiya jaey unmein nisf ushr ( beeswaan hissey ( hai.
2273,Abdullah-bin-Dinar ne Sulaiman-bin-Yasar se unhon-ne iraak-bin-Malik se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : musalman ke zimmey na iske ghulam mein sadqa ( zakat ( hai aur na iske ghodey mein.
2274,"Amr Naqid aur Zuhair-bin-Harab ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne hadis sunai unhon-ne kaha : hamein Ayub bin-Musa ne Mak-hool se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Sulaiman-bin-Yasar se unhon-ne iraak-bin-Malik se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki. Amr ne kaha : ( Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki aur Zuhair ne kaha : unhon-ne usey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tak pahuncha ya yani aap se bayan kiya. padhi. musalman par iske ghulam aur ghodey mein sadqa nahi."
2275,khaseem-bin-iraak-bin-Malik ne apne walid ( Irak bin Malik ( se unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ( uper zikr ki gaee hadis) ki tarah bayan kiya.
2276,Makhrima ne apne walid ( Bukair-bin-Abdullah ( se unhon-ne iraak-bin-Malik se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hadis bayan kartey huey suna ke aap ne farmaya : ( Malik par) ghulam (ke mamley ( mein sadqa fitr ke siwa koi sadqa nahi.
2277,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ko zakat ki wsoolii ke liye bheja to ( baad mein aap se) kaha gaya ke ibne-Jameel , Khalid-bin-Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chacha Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne zakat rok li hai) nahi di ( to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ibne-Jameel to iske ilawa kisi aur baat ka badla nahi ley raha ke wo pahley faqeer tha to Allah ne usey ghanii kar diya. rahe Khalid to tum un par zyadti kar rahe ho. unhon-ne apni zirahein aur hathiyar ( jangi saaz w saman ( Allah ki raah mein waqf kar rakhey hain. baqi rahe Abbas to unki zakat mere zimmey hai aur itni iske sath aur bhii. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey umr ! kya tumhen malum nahi, insan ka chacha uske bap jaisa hota hai? (unki zakat tum mujh se talab kar saktey they.)"
2278,"Imam Malik ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon par Ramazan ka sadqa fitr ( fitraana ( khajoor ya jo ka aik saa (fix) muqarrar kiya, wo ( fard ( musalmanon mein se aazad ho ya ghulam, mard ho ya aurat ."
2279,"Ubaidullah ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ghulam ya aazad, chhotey ya badey, har kisi par aik saa khajoor ya aik saa jo sadqae-fitr ( fitra) farz qarar diya."
2280,"Ayub ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aazad ho ya ghulam, mard ho ya aurat, har kisi par Ramazan ka sadqa khajoor ka aik saa ya jo ka aik saa muqarrar farmaya, kaha : logon ne gandam ka nisf saa us (jo (ke (eik saa ke) masaawii (baraber) qarar diya."
2281,Leis ne Naafe se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khajooron ka aik saa ya jo ka aik saa sadqae-fitr ( ada ( karne ka hukm diya. Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : to logon ne gandam ke do mudd us (jo (ke aik saa ke barabar qarar de liye.
2282,"zuhak ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ramazan mein musalmanon mein se har insan par aazad ya ghulam , mard ho ya aurat , chhota ho ya bada khajooron ka aik saa ya jo ka aik saa sadqae-fitr muqarrar farmaya."
2283,Zaid-bin-Aslam ne ayaaz-bin-Abdullah-bin-Sad-bin-abi-sarah se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna ham zakat al fitr tuaam ( gandam (ka aik saa ya jo ka aik saa ya khajooron ka aik saa ya paneer ka aik saa ya munaqqey ka aik saa nikala kartey they.
2284,"Dawood-bin-Qais ne ayaz-bin-Abdullah se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ham mein maujood they, to ham har chhotey, badey, aazad aur ghulam ki taraf se tuaam ( gandam (ka aik saa ya paneer ka aik saa ya jo ka aik saa ya khajooron ka aik saa ya munaqqey ka aik saa zakat-al-fitr ( fitraana ( nikaltey they aur ham usi ke mutabiq nikaltey rahe yahan tak ke hamarey paas ( ameerul-momeneen ( Muawiya-bin-abi-Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) Haj ya Umara ada karne ke liye tashrif laey aur member par logon ko khitab kiya aur logon se jo guftgu ki usmein ye bhi kaha : main ye samajhta hun ke Sham (Syria) se aaney wali) mahngii ( gandam ke do mudd (aadha saa) khajooron ke aik saa ke barabar hain iske baad logon ne us qaul ko apna liya. Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : lekin main, jab tak hon zindagi bhar hamesha isi tarah nikaaltaa rahunga jis tarah ( ahade-nabawii (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mein nikala karta tha.)"
2285,"Ismail-bin-Umayya ne kaha : mujhey ayaaz-bin-Abdullah-bin-Sad-bin-abi-sarah ne khabar di ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo keh rahe they ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki maujoodgii mein zakatul-fitr har chhotey, badey, aazad aur ghulam ki taraf se teen ( qisam ki) asnaaf se nikaltey they khajooron se aik saa, paneer se aik saa, aur jo se aik saa ham hamesha iske mutabiq nikaltey rahe yahan tak ke ameer Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ka daur aa gaya to unhon-ne ye raey pesh ki ke gandam ke do mudd khajooron ke aik saa ke barabar hain. Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : lekin main to usi (pahley tareeqey se) nikalta rahunga."
2286,"Haaris-bin-Abdur-Rehman-bin-abi-zubab ne ayaaz-bin-Abdullah-bin-abi-sarah se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : ham fitra un teen ajnaas se nikala kartey they paneer , khajoor aur jo . (yahi unki baniyaa di khurdanii (khane laayeq) ajnaas thin.)"
2287,ibne- Ajlan ne ayaaz-bin-Abdullah-bin-abi-sarah se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke jab Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne gandam ke aadhey saa ko khajooron ke saa ke barabar qarar diya to abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne is baat (ko manney ( se inkar kiya aur kaha : main fitrane mein iske siwa aur kuchh na nikalunga jo main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke daur mein nikala karta tha (aur wo hai) khajooron ka aik saa ya munaqqey ka aik saa ya jo ka aik saa ya paneer ka aik saa.
2288,Musa-bin-Aqba ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne fitraaney ke barey mein ye hukm diya ke usey Namaz eid ki taraf logon ke nikalney se pahley ada kar diya jaey.
2289,zuhak ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sadqae-fitr nikalney ke barey mein ye hukm diya ke usey logon ke eid ke nikalney se pahley ada kar diya jaey.
2290,"Hafs-bin-Maisra san'aanii ne Zaid-bin-Aslam se hadis bayan ki ke unko Abu-Saleh Zakwan ne khabar di ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo bhi soney aur chandi ka Malik unmein se (ya unki qeemat mein se) unka haq ( zakat ( ada nahi karta to jab qiyamat ka din hoga (unhein ( uske liye aag ki takhtiyan bana diya jaeyga aur unhein jahannam ki aag mein garm kiya jaeyga aur phir unse iske pahlu , uski peshani aur uski pusht ko daaghaa jaeyga. jab wo (takhtiyan) phir se (aag mein) jaaeingii, unhein phir se uske liye wapas laya jaeyga. us din jiski miqdar pachaas hazaar saal hai (ye amal musalsal hota rahega) yahan tak ke bandon ke darmyan faisla kar diya jaeyga. phir wo jannat ya dozakh ki taraf apna rasta dekh lega. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha gaya : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! oonton ka kya hukm hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi oonton ka Malik nahi jo unka haq ada nahi karta aur unka haq ye bhi hai ke unko pani pilaaney ke din ( zarurat mandon aur musaafiron ke liye) unka doodh nikala jaey. aur jab qiyamat ka din hoga us ( Malik ( ko aik wasee chatiyal maidan mein un ( oonton (ke samney bichhaa ( lita ( diya jaeyga. wo (oont duniya mein tadaad aur farbahii ke eitibaar se) jitney zyada se zyada waafir (motey-taazey) they us haalat mein hongey. wo unmein se doodh chhudaaey huey aik bachchey ko bhi gum nahi paaeyga. wo usey apne qadmon se raundein gey aur apne munh se kaatein gey. jab bhi unmein se pahlaa oont is par se guzar jaeyga to doosra is par wapas ley aaya jaeyga. ye us din mein) baar-baar ( hoga jiski miqdar pachaas hazaar saal hogi. yahan tak ke bandon ke darmyan faisla ho jaeyga aur usey jannat ya dozakh ki taraf iska rasta dikhaya jaeyga. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha gaya : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! to gaaey aur bakriyan ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aur na gaaey aur bakriyon ka koi Malik hoga jo unka haq ada nahi karta. magar jab qiyamat ka din hoga to usey unke samney wasee chatiyal maidan mein bichhaayaa (litaaya) jaeyga wo unmein se kisi aik ( janwar ( ko bhi gum nahi paaeyga . unmein koi ( gaaey ya bakri ( na mudey seengon wali hogi, na baghair seengon ke aur na hi koi tootey seengon wali hogi (sab seedhey tez seengon wali hongi ( wo usey apne seengon se maarein gii aur apne sumon se raundein gii. (ye mamla) us din mein (hoga) jo pachaas hazaar saal ke barabar hoga. jab pahlaa (janwar) guzar jaeyga to unka doosra (janwar wapas) ley aaya jaeyga yahan tak ke bandon ke darmyan faisla ho jaeyga. aur usey jannat ya dozakh ki taraf uska rasta dikhaya jaeyga. kaha gaya : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! to ghodey ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ghodey teen tarah ke hain : wo jo aadmi ke liye bojh hain, doosrey wo jo aadmi ke liye sat'ter (70) ( parda poshii ka baais ( hain. teesrey wo jo aadmi ke liye ajr w sawab ka baais hain. bojh aur gunah ka baais wo ghodey hain jinko unka Malik riyaakaarii , fakhr w ghurur , aur musalmanon ki dushmanii ke liye baandhtaa hai to ye ghodey uske liye bojh ( gunah ( hain. aur wo jo uskey liye parda poshii ka baais hain to wo (us) aadmi (ke ghodey hain) jisne unhein ( mauqa milney par) Allah ki raah main ( khud jihad karne ke liye) baandh rakha hai, phir wo unki pushton aur gardanon mein Allah ke haq ko nahi bhula to ye uske liye baais sat'ter (70) hain ( chahey usey jihad ka mauqa miley ya na miley). aur wo ghodey jo uske liye ajr w sawab ka baais hain to wo (us) aadmi (ke ghodey hain) jisne unhein Allah ki raah mein ahal Islam ki khaatir kisi charaagaah ya baagheechey mein baandh rakha hai (aur wo khud jihad par ja sakey ya na ja sakey unhein dusron ko jihad ke liye deta hai) ye ghodey us charaagaah ya baagh mein se jitna bhi khaaengey to us shakhs ke liye itni tadaad mein nekiyan likh di jaeyngi aur us shakhs ke liye unki leed aur peshab ki miqdar ke barabar (bhi) nekiyan likh di jaeyngi aur wo ghodey apni rassii tudwaakar aik-do teelon ki daud nahi lagaaein gey magar Allah Taala us shakhs ke liye unke qadmon ke nishanat aur leed ki tadaad ke barabar nekiyan likh dega aur na hi unka Malik unhein lekar kisi nehar par se guzrey ga aur wo ghodey us nehar mein se pani piyein gey jabke wo (Malik) unko pani pilaanaa ( bhi) nahi chahta magar Allah Taala us shakhs ke liye itni nekiyan likh dega jitna un ghodon ne pani piyaa. kaha gaya : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! aur gadhey ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mujh par gadhon ke barey mein us munfarid aur jaame aayat ke siwa koi cheez nazil nahi ki gaee :                       ( فَمَن يَعْمَلْ مِثْقَالَ ذَرَّ‌ةٍ خَيْرً‌ا يَرَ‌ہُ ۝وَمَن يَعْمَلْ مِثْقَالَ ذَرَّ‌ةٍ شَرًّ‌ا يَرَ‌هُ ( jo koi aik zarrey ki miqdar mein neki karega (qiyamat ke din) usey dekh lega aur jo koi aik zarrey ke barabar burai karega usey dekh lega."
2291,"Hisham-bin-Sad ne Zaid-bin-Aslam se isi sanad ke sath Hafs-bin-Maisra ki hadis ke aakhir tak iske ham mana riwayat bayan ki, albatta unhon-ne jo oonton ka Malik unka haq ada nahi karta kaha : aur) منهاحقها ( (aur mein se unka haq (ke alfaz nahi kahey aur unhon-ne ( bhi) apni hadis mein wo unmein se doodh chhudaaey huey aik bachchey ko bhi gum na paaeyga ke alfaz riwayat kiye hain aur isi tarah ( unse iske pahlu , peshani aur kamar ko daaghaa jaeyga ke bajaey)    ( يكوي بها جنباه وجبهته وظهره ) (iske donon pahlu , uski peshani aur kamar ko daaghaa jaaeyga) ke alfaz kahey ."
2292,"Abdul-Azeez-bin-Mukhtar ne kaha : hamein Suhail-bin-abi Saleh ne apne walid se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi bhi khazaaney ka Malik nahi jo uski zakat ada nahi karta, magar iske khazaaney ko jahannam ki aag mein tapaayaa jaeyga, phir uski takhtiyan banai jaeyngi aur unse iske donon pahluon aur peshani ko daaghaa jaeyga yahan tak ke Allah apne bandon ke darmyan faisla farma dega. (ye) us din mein hoga jiski miqdar pachaas hazaar saal ke barabar hai. phir usey jannat ya jahannam ki taraf iska rasta dikhaa diya jaeyga. aur koi bhi oonton ka Malik nahi jo unki zakat ada nahi karta magar usey un ( oonton (ke samney wasee chatiyal maidan mein litaya jaeyga jabke wo oont ( tadaad aur jasaamat mein) jitney zyada se zyada waafir (motey-taazey) they us haalat mein hongey (wo ( iske uper daud lagaaein gey . jab bhi unmein aakhirii oont guzrey ga pahlaa oont , is par dobara laya jaeyga . yahan tak ke Allah apne bandon ke darmyan faisla farmayega . (ye ( aik aisey din main (hoga) jo pachaas hazaar saal ke barabar hoga. phir usey jannat ya dozakh ki taraf uska rasta dikhaa diya jaeyga. aur jo bhi bakriyon ka Malik unki zakat ada nahi karta to usey wo waafir tareen haalat mein jis mein wo thin, unke samney aik wasee w areez chatiyal maidan mein bichhaa ( lita ( diya jaeyga. wo usey apne khuron se raundein gii aur apne seengon se maarein gii . unmein na koi mudey seengon wali hogi aur na baghair seengon ke. jab bhi aakhiri bakri guzregi usi waqt pehli dobara is par laai jaeygi. yahan tak ke Allah Taala aik aisey din mein jo pachaas hazaar saal ke barabar hai, apne bandon ke darmyan faisla kar dega. phir usey jannat ya dozakh ki taraf uska rasta dikhaya jaeyga. Suhel ne kaha : maine nahi janta ke aap ne gaaey ka tazkira farmaya ya nahi. sahaba ((Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen)) ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! to ghodey (ka kya hukm hai? (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qiyamat ke din tak khair , ghodon ki peshani mein hai. padhi. ya farmaya : ghodon ki peshani se bandhi hui hai. padhi. Suhel ne kaha : mujhey shak hai. padhi. ( farmaya ( ghodey teen qism ke hain. ye aik aadmi ke liye baais ajr hain, aik aadmi ke liye parda poshii ka baais hain aur aik ke liye bojh aur gunah ka sabab hain. wo ghodey jo us ( Malik (ke liye ajr (ka sabab ( hain to ( unka Malik ( wo aadmi hai jo unhein Allah ke rastey mein (jihad ke liye) paaltaa hai. aur taiyaar karta hai to ye ghodey koi cheez apne pet mein nahi daltey magar Allah uski wjah se uske liye ajr likh deta hai. agar wo unhein charaagaah mein charaataa hai to wo koi cheez bhi nahi khaatey . magar Allah Taala uski wjah se uske liye ajr likh deta hai. aur agar wo unhein kisi nehar se pani pilaataa hai to pani ke har qatrey ke badley jisey wo apne pet mein utaartey hain. uske liye ajr hai. yahan tak ke aap ne unke peshab aur leed karne mein bhi ajr milney ka tazkira kiya. padhi. aur agar ye ghodey aik ya do teelon (ka fasla ( daudiin to uske liye unke har qadam ke iwaz jo wo uthatey hain, ajr likh diya jata hai. aur wo insan jiske liye ye baais parda hain to wo aadmi hai jo unhein izzat w sharf aur zeenat ke taur par rakhta hai. aur wo tangi aur aasani (har haalat ( mein unki pushton aur unke peton ka haq nahi bhooltaa. raha wo aadmi jiske liye wo bojh hain to wo shakhs hai jo unhein naa-sapaas guzari ke taur par, ghurur aur takabbur karne aur logon ko dikhaaney ke liye rakhta hai to wahi hai jiske liye ye ghodey bojh ka baais hain. logon ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! to gadhey (unka kya hukm hai? (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala ne mujh par unke barey mein us munfarid aur jaame aayat ke siwa kuchh nazil nahi kiya : to jo koi zarra barabar neki karega wo usey dekh lega."
2293,Abdul-Azeez darawardi ne Suhel se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki aur) poori ( hadis bayan ki.
2294,Rooh-bin-Qasim ne kaha : hamein Suhail-bin-abi-Saleh ne isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur) aqsaa ( ) mudey huey seengon wali) ke bajaey ( azbaa ( ) tootey huey seengon wali) kaha : aur uske zariey se iska pahlu aur uski pusht daaghii jaeygi kaha aur peshani ka zikr nahi kiya.
2295,"bukair ne ( Abu-Saleh ( Zakwan se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab insan apne oonton mein Allah ka haq ya zakat ada nahi karta. padhi. aagey Suhel ki riwayat ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
2296,"ibne-Juraij ne kaha : mujhey abu-Zubair ne bataya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : koi oonton ka Malik nahi jo unke mamley mein is tarah nahi karta jis tarah unka haq hai magar wo qiyamat ke din apni intihai zyada tadaad mein aaeingey jo kabhi unki thi aur wo un ( oonton (ke samney wasee chatiyal maidan mein baithey ga aur wo usey apne agley qadmon aur apne paon se raundein gey. isi tarah koi gaaey ka Malik nahi jo unka haq ada nahi karta magar wo qiyamat ke din us se zyada se zyada tadaad mein aaein gii jo kabhi unki thi aur wo unke samney chatiyal maidan mein baithey ga. wo usey apne seengon se maarein gii aur apne pairon se raundein gii. aur isi tarah bakriyon ka koi Malik nahi jo unka haq ada nahi karta to wo qiyamat ke din apni zyada se zyada tadaad mein aaein gii jo kabhi unki thi aur wo unke samney wasee chatiyal maidan mein baithey ga aur wo usey apne seengon se maarein gii aur apne sumon se usey raundein gii aur unmein na koi seengon ke baghair hogi aur na hi koi tootey seengon wali hogi. aur koi (soney, chandi ke) khazaaney ka Malik nahi jo uska haq ada nahi karta magar qiyamat ke din uska khazaana ganjaa sanp bin kar aayega aur apna munh kholey huey iska ta'aqub karega, jab uske paas pahunchega to wo us se bhaagey ga , phir wo ( sanp ( usey awaz dega : apna khazaana ley lo jo tum ne ( duniya mein) chipa kar rakha tha. mujhey uski zarurat nahi hai. jab ( khazaaney wala ( dekhega us se bchney ki koi sura nahi to wo apna hath us ( sanp (ke munh mein dakhil karega, wo usey is tarah chabaaii ga jis tarah saandh chabaataa hai. abu-Zubair ne kaha : maine Ubaid-bin-Umair ko ye baat kehtey huey suna, phir ham ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se us ( hadis) ke barey mein puchha to unhon-ne isi tarah kaha jis tarah Ubaid-bin-Umair ne kaha. aur abu-Zubair ne kaha : maine Ubaid-bin-Umair ko kehtey huey suna aik aadmi ne kaha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! oonton ka haq kya hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : pani (pilaaney ke mauqe) par unka doodh dohnaa (aur logon ko pilaanaa) aur uska dol udhaar dena aur uska saand udhaar dena aur ontni ko doodh peeney ke liye dena aur Allah ki raah mein sawari ki khaatir dena."
2297,"Abdul-Malik ne abu-Zubair se, unhon-ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : oonton , gaaey aur bakriyon ka jo bhi Malik unka haq ada nahi karta to usey qiyamat ke din unke samney wasee chatiyal maidan mein bithaya jaeyga sumon wala janwar usey apne sumon se raundey ga aur seengon wala usey apne seengon se maarey ga. unmein se us din na koi (gaaey ya bakri) baghair seeng ke hogi aur na hi koi tootey huey seengon wali hogi. ham ne puchha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! unka haq kya hai? aap ne farmaya : unmein se nar ko juftii (jinsi milaap) ke liye denaa, unka dol udhaar denaa, unko doodh peeney ke liye denaa, unko pani ke ghaat par dohnaa (aur logon ko pilaanaa) aur Allah ki raah mein sawari ke liye denaa aur jo bhi sahibe-maal uski zakat ada nahi karta. to qiyamat ke din wo maal ganjey sanp ki shakl ikhtiyar kar lega. iska Malik jahan jaeyga wo iske peechhey laga rahega aur wo us se bhaagey ga. usey kaha jaeyga : ye tera wahi maal hai jis main to kanjoosii kiya karta tha. jab wo dekhega ke us se bchney ki koi sura nahi hai to wo apna hath uskey munh mein dakhil karega, wo usey is tarah chabaaii ga jis tarah oont (chaarey ko) chabaataa hai."
2298,"abdul-Wahid-bin-Ziyad ne kaha : hamein Muhammad-bin-abi-Ismail ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Abdur-Rehman-Hilaal-bin-absa ne Hazrat Jareer-bin-Abdullaah (Raziallahu anhu) taala se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : kuchh badwi log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur kehney lagey : kuchh zakat wasool karne waley log hamarey paas aatey hain aur ham par zulm kartey hain to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : apni zakat wasool karne walon ko razi kiya karo. Hazrat Jarir (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : jab se maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye hadis suni hai to mere paas se jo koi zakat wasool karne wala gaya, razi gaya."
2299,"abdur-Raheem-bin-Sulaiman, Yahya-bin-Saeed aur abu-Usama sab ne Muhammad-bin-Ismail se uper zikr ki gaee sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
2300,"Wakee ne kaha : Aamash ne hamein Ma'roor-bin-Suwed ke hawale se Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas hazir hua, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Kabey ke saaey mein tashrif farma they jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey dekha to farmaya :  Kaba ke rab ki qism ! wahi log sabse zyada khasaara uthaney waley hain. kaha : main aa kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas betha (hi tha) aur itminan se betha hi na tha ke khada ho gaya aur maine kaha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! mere maan-baap Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par qurbaan wo kon log hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wo zyada maaldaar log hain, siwaey uske jis ne, apne aagey , apne peechhey , apne daain , apne baain , aisey , aisey aur aisey kaha ( ley lo, ley lo (aur aisey log bahut kam hain. jo bhi oonton , gaayon ya bakriyon ka Malik unki zakat ada nahi karta to wo qiyamat ke din is tarah badi aur motii ho kar aaein gii jitni zyada se zyada thin. usey apne seengon se maarein gii aur apne khuron se raundein gii jab bhi unmein se aakhiri guzar kar jaeygi, pehli us (ke sar ( par wapas aa jaeygi yahan tak ke logon ke darmyan faisla kar diya jaeyga."
2301,"abu-Muawiya ne Aamash se, unhon-ne ma'roor se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas pahuncha , aap Kaba ke saaey mein tashrif farma they. aagey Wakee ki riwayat ki tarah hai, albatta (is mein hai ke) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya is zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai ! zamin par jo bhi aadmi faut hota hai aur aisey oont , gaaey ya bakriyan peechhey chhod jata hai jinki us ne zakat ada nahi ki."
2302,Rabe-bin-Muslim ne Muhammad-bin-Ziyad se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mere liye ye baat khushi ka baais nahi ke mere paas Uhud pahaad ke barabar sona ho aur tesraa din mujh par is tarah aaey ke mere paas usmein se koi Dinar bacha hua maujood ho siwaey us Dinar ke jis ko main apna qarz chukaaney ke liye rakh loon.
2303,"Shoba ne Muhammad-bin-Ziyad se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kartey suna. padhi. usi ki tarah ."
2304,"Aamash ne Zaid-bin-Wahab se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : (eik raat ( isha ke waqt Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Madina ki kali pathreelii zamin par chal raha tha aur ham Uhud pahaad ko dekh rahe they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : Abu-Zar ! maine kaha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hazir hun ! farmaya : mujhey ye pasand nahi hai ke ye (pahaad) ahad mere paas soney ka ho aur main us haalat mein teesri Sham karun ke mere paas usmein se aik Dinar bacha hua maujood ho siwaey us Dinar ke jo maine qarz (ki adaaeygi (ke liye bachaya ho, aur main usey Allah ke bandon mein is tarah ( kharch ( karun. aap ne apne samney donon hathon se bhar kar dalney ka ishara kiya. is tarah ( kharch ( karun. daain taraf se. . padhi. is tarah . baain taraf se. . padhi. ( Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : phir ham chaley to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Abu-Zar ! maine kaha : Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hazir hun ! aap ne farmaya : yaqinan zyada maaldaar hi qiyamat ke din kam samaan waley hongey, magar wo jisne is tarah , is tarah aur is tarah ( kharch ( kiya. jis tarah aap ne pehli baar kiya tha. Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ham phir chaley. aap ne farmaya : Abu-Zar ! mere wapas aaney tak isi haalat mein thahrey rehna. kaha : aap chaley yahan tak ke meri nazron se ojhal ho gaey. maine shor sa suna, awaz suni to maine dil mein kaha shayad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko koi cheez pesh aa gaee hai, chunanche maine peechhey janey ka irada kar liya phir mujhey aap ka ye farman yad aa gaya : mere aaney tak yahan se na hatna to maine aap ka intizar kiya, jab aap waapas tashrif laey to maine jo ( kuchh ( suna tha aapko bataya . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wo Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) they, mere paas aaey aur bataya ke aap ki ummat ka jo fard is haal mein faut hoga ke kisi cheez ko Allah ke sath shirk na karta tha wo jannat mein dakhil hoga. maine puchha : chahey us ne zina kiya ho aur chori ki ho? unhon-ne kaha : chahey us ne zina kiya ho aur chori ki ho."
2305,"Abdul-Azeez-bin-rafeea' ne Zaid-bin-Wahab se aur unhon-ne Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main aik raat ( ghar se) bahar nikla to achcha dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) akeley ja rahe hain, aap ke sath koi insan nahi to maine khayal kiya ke aap is baat ko na-pasand kar rahe hain ke koi aap ke sath chaley. chunanche main chaand ke saaey mein chalney laga, aap mudey to mujhey dekh liya aur farmaya : ye kon hai? maine kaha : Abu-Zar hon, Allah mujhey aap par qurbaan karey ! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Abu-Zar ! aa jao . kaha : main kuchh der aap ke sath chala to aap ne farmaya : be-shak zyada maal waley hi qiyamat ke din kam (samaan) hongey, siwaey unke jinko Allah ne maal ata farmaya : aur unhon-ne usey daain , baain aur aagey , peechhey uda daala aur is mein neki ke kaam kiye. mein aik ghadi aap ke sath chalta raha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : yahan baith jao . aap ne mujhey aik hamwaar zamin mein bitha diya jiske gird patthar they aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey farmaya : yahin baithey rehna yahan tak ke main tumharey paas lot aaoon. aap pathreeley maidan (harrey) mein chal padey yahan tak ke meri nazron se ojhal ho gaey, aap mujh se door rukey rahe aur zyada der kar di, phir maine aap ki awaz suni jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) meri taraf aatey huey farma rahe they : chahe us ne chori ki ho ya zina kiya ho. jab aap tashrif ley aaey to main sabr na kar saka maine kaha : aey Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! Allah mujhey aap par nisaar farmaai ! aap siyah pattharon ke maidan ( Harra (ke kinarey kis se guftgu farma rahe they? maine to kisi ko nahi suna jo aapko jawab de raha ho. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wo Jibreel (Alaihissalam) they jo siyah pattharon ke kinarey mere samney aaey aur kaha : apni ummat ko basharat de dijiye ki jo koi is haalat mein marey ga ke Allah ke sath kisi cheez ko Sharik nahi thahraataa hoga wo jannat mein dakhil hoga. maine kaha : aey Jibreel ! chahey us ne chori ki ho ya zina kiya ho? unhon-ne kaha : haan ! farmaya : maine phir kaha : chahe us ne chori ki ho chahe us ne zina kiya ho? unhon-ne kaha : haan. maine phir ( teesri baar ( puchha : chahe us ne chori ki ho chahe us ne zina kiya ho? unhon-ne kaha : haan , chahe us ne sharab (bhi) pi ho."
2306,"abul-Ala ne Hazrat ahnaf-bin-Qais (Rahmatullahi-alaih) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : main Madina aaya to main qureshi sardaaron ke aik halqey mein betha hua tha ke achcha khurdarey kapdon, gatthey huey jism aur sakht chehrey wala aik aadmi aaya aur unke sar par khada ho gaya aur kehney laga. maal w daulat jama karne walon ko us taptey huey patthar ki basharat suna do jis ko jahannam ki aag mein garm kiya jaeyga aur usey unke aik fard ki nauke pistaan par rakha jaeyga yahan tak ke wo uske donon kandhon ki baareek haddiyon se lahraataa hua nikal jaeyga aur usey uske shaanon ki baareek haddiyon par rakha jaeyga yahan tak ke wo uske pistaanon ke saron se harkat karta hua nikal jaeyga ( Ahnaf ne) kaha : is par logon ne apne sar jhukaa liye aur maine unmein se kisi ko na dekha ke usey koi jawab diya ho, kaha : phir wo lota aur maine uska peechhaa kiya yahan tak ke wo aik sutoon ke sath ( tek laga kar) baith gaya maine kaha : aap ne unhein jo kuchh kaha hai maine unhein usko naa pasand kartey huey hi dekha hai unhon-ne kaha : ye log kuchh samajhtey nahi mere khaleel abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey bulaya maine labbaik kaha to aap ne farmaya : kya tum ahad ( pahaad ( ko dekhtey ho? maine dekha ke mujh par kitna suraj baqi hai main samajh raha tha ke aap mujhey apni kisi zarurat ke liye bhejna chahtey hain chunaanche maine kaha, main usey dekh raha hun. to aap ne farmaya : mere liye ye baat baaise-musarrat na hogi ke mere paas iske barabar sona ho aur main teen dinaron ke siwa us sarey ( soney ( ko kharch ( bhi) kar daalun . phir ye log hain duniya jama kartey hain kuchh aql nahi kartey. maine unse puchha aap ka apne ( hukmaraan ( qureshi bhaiyon ke sath kiya mamla hai aap apni zarurat ke liye na unke paas jatey hain aur na unse kuchh letey hain? unhon-ne jawab diya nahi tumharey parwardigar ki qism ! na main unse duniya ki koi cheez maangon ga na hi unse kisi deeni masley ke barey mein poochhoon ga yahan tak ke main Allah aur uske Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ja miloon."
2307,"khuledul-asree ne Hazrat ahnaf-bin-Qais (Rahmatullahi-alaih) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha, main Quraish ki aik jamat mein maujood tha ke Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ye kehtey huey guzrey : maal jama karne walon ko) aag ke) un daaghon ki basharat suna do jo unki pushton par lagaey jaeinge aur unke pahluon se niklengey aur un daaghon ki jo unki gaddiyon ki taraf se lagaey jaeinge aur unki peshaaniyon se niklengey kaha : phir wo alag thalag ho kar baith gaey maine puchha ye sahib kon hain? logon ne bataya ye Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) hain main uth kar unke paas chala gaya aur puchha kya baat thi jo abhi thodi der pahley maine suni aap keh rahe they? unhon-ne jawab diya maine is baat ke siwa kuchh nahi kaha jo maine unke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni. kaha maine puchha ( hukumat se milney waale) atiye ( wazeefey (ke barey mein aap kya kehtey hain? unhon-ne jawab diya usey ley lo kyonke aaj ye maoonat ( madad ( hai aur jab ye tumharey Deen ki qeemat thahrein to unhein chhod dena."
2308,"Zuhair-bin-Harab aur Muhammad-bin-Abdullah-bin-Numair ne kaha : Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne hamein abu Zinad se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne ea'raaj se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki wo us ( silsile sanad) ko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tak ley jatey they ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala ne farmaya hai aey Adam ke betey ! to kharch kar mein tujh par kharch karunga aur aap ne farmaya : Allah ka dayan hath ( achi tarah) bharaa hua hai. ibne-Numair ne ( Mulai (ke bajaey ( milaan ( (ka lafz ( kaha, padhi. iska faiz jari rehta hai din ho ya raat koi cheez usmein kami nahi karti."
2309,"Wahab-bin-Munabbah ke bhai Hammam-bin-Munabbah se riwayat hai kaha : ye hadisein hain jo hamein Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kiin phir unhon-ne chand hadisein bayan kiin unmein se aik ye bhi thi aur) Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala ne mujh se kaha hai kharch karo main tum par kharch karunga aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah ka dayan hath bharaa hua, din raat ata ki barish barsaey wala hai is mein koi cheez kami nahi karti . kya tum ne dekha aasman w zamin ki takhleeq se lekar (ab tak) us ne kitna kharch kiya hai? jo kuchh iske daain hath mein hai, us ( ata ( ne usmein koi kami nahi ki. aap ne farmaya : uska arsh pani par hai, uske doosrey hath mein qabza (ya waapsii ki quwwat ( hai wo ( jisey chahta hai) buland karta hai aur) jisey chahta hai) past karta hai."
2310,"abu-Qilaba ne abu-Asma (Rahbi) se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : behtreen Dinar jisey insan kharch karta hai wo Dinar hai jisey wo apne ahal w ayaal par kharch karta hai aur wo Dinar hai jisey insan Allah ki raah mein (jihad karne ke liye) apne janwar ( sawari ( par kharch karta hai aur wo Dinar hai jisey wo Allah ke rastey main apne sathiyon par kharch karta hai. abu-Qilaba ne kaha : aap ne ahal w ayaal se shuruaat farmai, phir abu-Qilaba ne kaha : ajr mein us aadmi se badh kar kon ho sakta hai jo chhotey bachchon par kharch karta hai wo unko ( sawal ki) zillat se bachaataa hai ya Allah uske zariey se unhein fayda pahunchata hai aur ghanii karta hai."
2311,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya (jin dinaron par ajr milta hai unmein se) aik Dinar wo hai jisey to ne Allah ki raah mein kharch kiya. aik Dinar wo hai jisey to ne kisi ki gardan (ki aazadi (ke liye kharch kiya. aik Dinar wo hai jisey to ne miskeen par sadqa kiya aur aik Dinar wo hai jisey to ne apne ghar walon par kharch kiya. inmein sabse azeem ajr us Dinar ka hai jisey to ne apne ahal par kharch kiya.
2312,khaisma se riwayat hai kaha : ham Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas baithey huey they ke achcha unka kaarinda ( menajer ( unke paas aaya wo andar dakhil hua to unhon-ne puchha : (kya ( tum ne ghulaamon ko unka rozeena de diya hai? us ne jawab diya nahi unhon-ne kaha : jao unhein do. (kyonke) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : insan ke liye itna gunah hi kafi hai ke wo jinki khuraak ka Malik hai unhein na de.
2313,Leis ne hamein abu-Zubair se khabar di aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki. unhon-ne kaha : banu- azra ke aik aadmi ne aik ghulam ko apne baad aazadi di (ke mere marney ke baad wo aazad hoga ( ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tak pahunchi to aap ne puchha : kya tumharey paas iske ilawa bhi koi maal hai? usne kaha : nahi is par aap ne farmaya : is ( ghulam ( ko mujh se kon khareedega ? to usey Naeem bin-Abdullah Adwi (Raziallahu anhu) ne aath-so ( 800 ( dirham mein khareed liya aur dirham la kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko pesh kar diye. iske baad aap ne farmaya : apne aap se shuruaat karo khud par sadqa karo agar kuchh bach jaey to tumharey ghar walon ke liye hai agar tumharey ghar walon se kuchh bach jaey to tumharey qaraabat daaron ke liye hai aur agar tumharey qaraabat daaron se kuchh bach jaey to us taraf aur us taraf kharch karo. ( rawi ne kaha : (aap ishaarey se keh rahe they ke apne samney apne daain aur apne baain ( kharch karo).
2314,"Ayub ne abu-Zubair se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ke Ansar mein se abu mazkoor naam ke aik aadmi ne apne ghulam ko jisey Yaqoob kaha jata tha, apne marney ke baad aazad qarar diya. aagey unhon-ne Leis ki hadis ke ham mana hadis bayan ki."
2315,"Ishaq-bin-Abdullah-bin-abi-Talha se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo farma rahe they : abu Talha Madina mein kisi bhi Ansari se zyada maaldaar they, unke maal mein se beeri-haa-wala baagh unhein sabse zyada pasand tha jo masjide-Nabawi ke samney waaqe tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usmein tashrif ley jatey aur iska umda pani nosh farmatey. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : jab ye aayat nazil hui : tum neki hasil nahi kar sakogey jab tak apni mahboob cheez ( Allah ki raah mein) kharch na karogey. abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) uth kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas gaey aur kaha : Allah Taala apni kitab mein farmatey hain ke : tum neki hasil nahi kar sakogey yahan tak ke apni pasandida cheez ( Allah ki raah mein) kharch karo. mujhey apne amwaal mein se sabse zyada beeri-haa pasand hai aur wo Allah ke liye sadqa hai, mujhey iske achchhey badley aur Allah ke yahan zakheera (ke taur par mehfooz (ho janey ki ummeed hai. aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! aap usey jahan chaahein rakhein. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bahut khub , ye sood mand maal hai, ye nafa bakhsh maal hai, jo tum ne iske barey mein kaha maine sun liya hai aur meri raey ye hai ke tum isey (apne ( qaraabat daaron ko de do. to abbu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey apne azeezon aur apne chacha ke beton mein taqseem kar diya."
2316,"Sabit ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : jab ye aayat nazil hui : tum neki (ki haqiqi lazzat ( hasil nahi kar sakogey yahan tak ke apni mahboob tareen cheez ( Allah ki raah mein) kharch kar do. (to ( abu Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main apne parwardigar ko dekhta hun ke wo ham se maal ka mutalba kar raha hai. lihaza aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! main aapko gawah banata hun ke maine apni zamin beeri-haa Allah Taala ke liye waqf kar di. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : usey apne rishte-daaron ko de do. to unhon-ne wo Hazrat Hassaan-bin-Saabit aur Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ko de di."
2317,(Ummul-Momenin) Hazrat Memuna-bint-Haaris (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke daur main apni aik londi ko aazad kiya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas iska tazkira kiya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar tum usey apne mamuon ko de diiyatein to ye (kaam) tumharey ajr ko bada kar deta.
2318,"abu-Ahwas ne Aamash se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Waail se, unhon-ne Amr-bin-Haris se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) (bin-Masood ( ki biwi Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ( bint-Abdullah-bin-Ubai Muawiya ( se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey aurton ki jamat ! sadqa karo, agarche apne zewaraat se hi kyon na ho. kaha : to main (apne khawind ( Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas wapas aai aur kaha : tum kam maya aadmi ho aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein sadqa karne ka hukm diya hai. lihaza tum Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas ja kar aap se poochh lo agar us (ko tumhen diye ( se meri taraf se ada ho jaeyga (to theek ( warna mein usey tumharey ilawa dusron ki taraf bhej dun gii , kaha : to Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujh se kaha : balke tum khud hi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas chali jao . unhon-ne kaha : main gaee to us waqt aik aur Ansari aurat bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke darwazey par khadi thi aur) masla malum karne ke hawale se) uski zarurat bhi wahi thi jo meri thi, aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko haibat ata ki gaee thi. kaha : Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) nikal kar hamari taraf aaey to ham ne unse kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein jao aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bataao ke darwazey par do a'urtey hain aap se poochh rahi hain ke unki taraf se unke khaawindon aur un yateem bachchon par jo unki kifaalat mein hain, sadqa jaaiz hai? aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye na batana ke ham kon hain? Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas hazir huey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se poochha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : wo donon kon hain? unhon-ne kaha : aik Ansari aurat hai aur aik Zenab hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha : zainabon mein se kon si ? unhon-ne kaha : Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi . to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse kaha : unke liye do ajr hain : (eik ( qaraabat nibhaaney ka ajr aur (doosra) sadqa karne ka ajr ."
2319,"Umar-bin-Hafs-bin-Ghiyas ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Aamash se baqi bachi pichhli sanad ke sath riwayat ki. (Aamash ne) kaha : maine (ye hadis) Ibrahim Nakhai se bayan ki to unhon-ne mujhey abu-ubaida se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Amr-bin-Haris se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi Zenab (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, bilkul usi (mazkooh bula riwayat) ki tarah , aur kaha : unhon ( Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ( ne kaha : main masjid mein thi (is darwazey par jo masjid mein tha) Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ke bataaney par) mujhey dekha to farmaya : sadqa karo, chahey apne zewaraat hi se kyon na ho. Aamash ne baqi hadis abu-Ahwas ki (uper zikr ki gaee) riwayat ke ham mana bayan ki hai."
2320,"abu-Usama ne kaha : hamein Hisham-bin-Urwa ne apne walid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Zainab-binte-abi-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! kya abu-Salma (Raziallahu anhu) ki aulad par kharch karne mein mere liye ajr hai? main un par kharch kar tii hon, mein unhein aisey , aisey chhodney wali nahi hun, wo mere bachchey hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : haan , tumharey liye un mein, jo tum un par kharch karogii , ajr hai."
2321,Ali-bin-Mus'hir aur Mamar ( Rashid ( donon ne baqi bachi isi sanad ke sath Hisham-bin-Urwa se usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
2322,"Ubaidullah-bin-Muaz Anbari ke walid ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Shoba ne Adii-bin-Sabit se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin Yazeed se, unhon-ne Hazrat abu Masood Badri (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : musalman jab apne ahal-w-ayaal par kharch karta hai aur us se Allah ki raza chahta hai to wo uske liye sadqa hai."
2323,Muhammad-bin-Jafar aur Wakee donon ne baqi bachi isi sanad ke sath Shoba se yahi hadis bayan ki.
2324,"Abdullah-bin-Idris ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se, unhon-ne apne walid se, aur unhon-ne Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine puchha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! meri walida mere paas aai hain aur (sila rehmii ki) khahish mand hain. ya (khali hath waapsii se) dari hui hain. kya main unse sila rehmii karun? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : haan."
2325,"Hisham ke aik aur shagird abu-Usama ne isi sanad ke sath Hazrat Asma-binte-abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha Quraish ke sath muaahidey ke zamaney mein, jab aap ne unse muaahida suleh kiya tha, meri walida aaein, wo mushrik thin to maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! meri walida mere paas aai hain aur (mujh se sila rehmii ki) ummeed rakhti hain to kya main apni maan se sila rehmii karun? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : haan , apni maa ke sath sila rehmii karo."
2326,Muhammad-bin-Bishr ne kaha : ham se Hisham ne apne walid ke hawale se Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se hadis bayan ki ke aik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! meri walida achcha wafat pa gaee hain aur unhon-ne koi wasiiyat nahi ki. mera unke barey mein guman hai ke agar boltiin to wo zaroor sadqa kartin. agar (ab) main unki taraf se sadqa karun to kya unhein ajr milega? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : haan.
2327,"Yahya-bin-Saeed, abu-Usama  Ali-bin-Mus'hir aur Shuaib-bin-Ishaq sab ne Hisham se baqi bachi isi sanad ke sath (usi ki tarah) riwayat bayan ki. abu-Usama ki hadis main ( ولم توص ( (is ne wasiiyat nahi ki) ke alfaz hain, jis tarah ibne-Bishr ne kaha hai. (jabke) baqi rawiyon ne ye alfaz bayan nahi kiye."
2328,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed aur abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne apni apni sanad ke sath Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki. Quteba ki hadis mein hai tumharey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aur ibne-Abi-Sheba ne kaha : Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat hai, padhi. har neki sadqa hai."
2329,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke kuchh sathiyon ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! zyada maal rakhney waley ajr w sawab le gaey wo hamari tarah Namaz padhtey hain aur hamari tarah rozey rakhtey hain aur apne zarurat se zayed maalon se sadqa kartey hain (jo ham nahi kar saktey). Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya Allah Taala ne tumharey liye aisi cheez nahi banai jis se tum sadqa kar sako? be-shak har baar Subhan-Allah kehna sadqa hai, har baar Allahu-akbar kehna sadqa hai, har baar  Alhmdulillah kehna sadqa hai, har dafa لا الہ الا اللہ (la-ilaha-il-lalah) kehna sadqa hai, neki ki talqeen karna sadqa hai aur burai se rokna sadqa hai aur (biwi se mubashrat kartey huey) tumharey uzu (khaas ang) mein sadqa hai. sahaba kiram ne puchha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! ham mein se koi apni khahish poori karta hai to kya is mein bhi ajr milta hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bataao agar wo ye ( khahish ( haram jagah poori karta to kya usey is par gunah ne hota ? isi tarah jab wo usey halal jagah poori karta hai to uske liye ajr hai."
2330,"abu-Tooba-rabe'e-bin-Naafe ne bayan kiya, kaha : hamein Muawiya-bin-Salam ne Zaid se hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne abu-salam ko bayan kartey huey suna. wo keh rahe they mujhey Abdullah-bin-farukh ne hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko farmatey huey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bani-Adam mein se har insan ko teen so sath mafaasil (jodon) par paida kiya gaya hai to jisne takbeer kahi , Allah ki hamd kahi , Allah ki whdaniyat ka iqrar kiya, Allah ki tasbeeh kahi , Allah se maghfirat mangi , logon ke rastey se koi patthar hataya, logon ke rastey se kaantaa ya haddi (hataaii), neki ka hukm diya ya burai se rokaa, un teen so sath jodon ki tadaad ke barabar, to wo us din is tarah chalega ke wo apne aapko dozakh ki aag se door kar chuka hoga. abu-Tooba ne kaha : kabhi-kabhi unhon (Muaawiya) ne ( يمشي ( chalega ke bajaey) (يمسي) (Sham ya din ka ikhtitaam karega) kaha."
2331,"Yahya-bin-Hassan ne kaha : hamein Muawiya (bin-salam) ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Zaid ke bhai ne isi sanad ke sath usi (pichhli hadis) ki manind (tarah) khabar di magar unhon-ne kaha : ( اوامربالمعروف ( (ya neki ka hukm diya) ke bajaey aur kaha : ( فانه يمسي يومئذ ( (wo us din us haalat mein Sham karega)."
2332,"Yahya ne Zaid-bin-salam se aur unhon-ne apne dada abu-salam se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Abdullah-bin-farukh ne hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko ye kehtey huey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : har insan ko paida kiya gaya hai. aagey Zaid se Muawiya ki riwayat ki tarah bayan kiya aur kaha : ( فانه يمشي يومئيذ ( to wo us din chalega ."
2333,"abu-Usama ne Shoba se, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-abi-burda se, unhon-ne apne walid ke waastey se apne dada (abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu)) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : har musalman par sadqa lazim hai, kaha gaya : aap ka kya khayal hai agar usey (sadqa karne ke liye koi cheez ( na miley? farmaya : apne hathon se kaam karke apne aapko fayda pahunchaaey aur sadqa (bhi) kare. usne kaha :  aap kya farmatey hain agar wo uski istitaat na rakhey? farmaya : be bas zarurat mand ki madad kare. kaha, aap se kaha gaya : dekhiye ! agar wo uski bhi istitaat na rakhey? farmaya : neki ya bhalai ka hukm de. kaha : dekhiye agar wo aisa bhi na kar sakey? farmaya : wo (apne aapko ( shar se rok ley , ye bhi sadqa hai."
2334,Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne isi sanad ke sath (yahi) hadis bayan ki.
2335,"Hammam-bin-Munabba se riwayat hai, kaha : ye hadisein hain jo Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein Muhammad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kin. unhon-ne kuchh hadisein bayan kiin unmein se ye bhi hai : aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya logon ke har jod par har roz , jis mein suraj tuloo hota hai, sadqa hai. farmaya : tum do (aadmiyon) ke darmyan adl karo (ye ( sadqa hai. aur tumhara kisi aadmi ki, iske janwar ke mutaalliq madad karna ke usey is par Sawar kara do ya uski khaatir sawari par uska saman utha kar rakho, (ye bhi) sadqa hai. farmaya : achi baat sadqa hai aur har qadam jis se tum masjid ki taraf chaltey ho, sadqa hai aur tum rastey se takleef deh cheez ko hata do (ye bhi) sadqa hai."
2336,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi din nahi jis mein bandey subah kartey hain magar (is mein aasman se) do Farishtey utartey hain, unmein se aik kehta hai : aey Allah ! kharch karne waley ko (behtreen) badal ata farma aur doosra kehta hai : aey Allah ! rokney waley ka (maal ( talaf (halak) kar de."
2337,"saiyedna Haarisa-bin-Wahab (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey they : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se, ke farmatey they : ''sadqa do qareeb hai ke aisa waqt aa jaeyga ke aadmi apna sadqa lekar niklega aur jis ko dene lagega wo kahega agar tum kal latey to main ley leta magar aaj to mujhey haajat nahi hai gharaz koi na milega jo usey qabool kar ley.''"
2338,"Abdullah-bin-baraad-Ash'arii aur abu-Kuraib Muhammad-bin-Alaa donon ne kaha : hamein abu-Usama ne bareed se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Burda se unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : logon par yaqinan aisa waqt aayega jis mein aadmi soney ka sadqa lekar ghoomey ga phir usey koi aisa aadmi nahi milega jo usey us se ley-ley. aur mardon ki qillat aur aurton ki kasarat ki wjah se aisa akelaa aadmi dekha jaeyga jiske peechhey chalis (40) auratein hongi jo uski panah ley rahi hongi . ibne- baraad ki riwayat main ( aisa akelaa aadmi dekha jaeyga ki jagah ( وتري رجل ( (aur tum aisey aadmi ko dekhogey ( hai."
2339,Suhel ke walid ( Abu-Saleh ( ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya qiyamat qaaim nahi hogi yahan tak ke maal badh jaeyga aur) pani ki tarah) bahney lagega aur aadmi apne maal ki zakat lekar niklega to usey aik shakhs bhi nahi milega jo usey uski taraf se qabool kar ley aur yahan tak ke Arab ki sar zamin dobaara charaagahon aur nehron mein badal jaeygi.
2340,"abu Yunus ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : qiyamat qaaim nahi hogi yahan tak ke tumharey yahaan maal ki faraawaanii hogi, wo maal (pani ki tarah) bahey ga yahan tak ke maal ke Malik ko ye fikr laahiq hogi ke us se us (maal) ko bataur sadqa kon qabool karega? aik aadmi ko usey leney ke liye bulaya jaeyga to wo kahega : mujhey iski koi zarurat nahi."
2341,"abu-Hazim ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : zamin apne jigar ke tukdey soney aur chandi ke sutunon ki sura mein ugal degi to qaatil aayega aur kahega kya iski khaatir maine qatl kiya tha? rishte-daari todney wala aa kar kahega : kya iske sabab maine qata' rehmii ki thi? chor aa kar kahega : kya iske sabab mera hath kaataa gaya tha? phir wo us maal ko chhod dengey aur is mein se kuchh nahi lengey."
2342,Saeed-bin-Yasar se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo keh rahe they Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi shakhs pakeeza maal se koi sadqa nahi karta aur Allah Taala pakeeza maal hi qabool farmata hai magar wo Rehman usey apne daain hath mein leta hai chahey wo khajoor ka aik daa na ho to wo us Rehman ki hatheli mein phaltaa phooltaa hai yahan tak ke pahaad se bhi bada ho jata hai bilkul isi tarah jis tarah tum mein se koi apne bachherey ya oont ke bachchey ko paalta hai.
2343,"Yaqoob-bin-Abdur-Rehman al-qari ne Suhel se unhon-ne apne walid ( Abu-Saleh ( se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya koi shakhs apni pakeeza kamaai se aik khajoor bhi kharch nahi karta magar Allah usey apne daahaney hath se qabool karta hai aur usey is tarah paaltaa hai jis tarah tum mein se koi apne bachherey ya oont ke bachchey ko paaltaa hai. yahan tak ke wo ( khajoor ( pahaad ki tarah ya us se bhi badi ho jati hai."
2344,Rooh-bin-Qasim aur Sulaiman-bin-Bilal donon ne Suhel se isi sanad ke sath (mazkura bula ( hadis bayan ki. Rooh ki hadis mein hai. ( من الكسب الطيب فيضعها في حقها ( ) halal kamaaii se sadqa karta hai phir usko wahan lagata hai jahan iska haq hai) aur Sulaiman ki hadis mein hai) فيضعها في موضعها ( (aur usey uski jagah par kharch karta hai).
2345,Hisham-bin-Sad ne Zaid-bin-Aslam se unhon-ne Abu-Saleh se unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se isi tarah riwayat ki jis tarah Suhel se Yaqoob ki hadis hai.
2346,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai unhon-ne kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey logo ! Allah Taala paak hai aur paak (maal (ke siwa (koii maal ( qabool nahi karta. Allah ne mominon ko bhi usi baat ka hukm diya jiska rasulon ko hukm diya, Allah Taala ne farmaya : aey paighambaraane kiram ! paak cheezein khaao aur nek kaam karo jo amal tum kartey ho, main usey achi tarah jaanney wala hun aur farmaya aey momino ! jo paak rizq ham ne tumhen inayat farmaya hai is mein se khaao . phir aap ne aik aadmi ka zikr kiya : jo lamba safar karta hai baal paraaganda aur jism ghubaar aalud hai. (dua ke liye aasman ki taraf apne donon hath phailaataa hai aey mere rab aey mere rab! jabke iska khana haram ka hai, iska peenaa haram ka hai, iska libaas haram ka hai, aur usko ghizaa haram ki mili hai to uski dua kahan se qabool hogi ! ."
2347,"Abdullah-bin-ma'qil ne Hazrat Adii-bin-Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : tum mein se jo shakhs aag se mehfooz rehney ki taaqat rakhey chahey khajoor ke aik tukdey ke zariey se kyon na ho, wo zaroor (aisa) kare."
2348,"Ali-bin-Hujr-Sadi , Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim aur Ali-bin-khashram mein se Ali-bin-hijr ne kaha : hamein Esa-bin-Yonus ne hadis bayan ki aur baqi donon ne kaha : hamein khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Aamash ne khaisma ke waastey se Hazrat Adii-bin-Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi nahi magar an-qareeb Allah is tarah is se baat karega ke iske aur Allah Taala ke darmyan koi tarjuman nahi hoga aur apni daain taraf dekhega to usey wahi kuchh nazar aayega jo usney aagey bheja aur apni baain taraf dekhega to wahi kuchh dikhai dega jo usney aagey bheja aur apne aagey dekhega to usey apne munh ke samney aag dikhai degi isliye aag se bacho agarche aadhi khajoor ke zariey hi se kyon na ho. (Ali)-bin-hijr ne izafa kiya : Aamash ne kaha : mujhey Amr-bin-Murra ne khaisma se usi jaisi hadis bayan ki aur is mein izafa kiya : chahey pakeeza bol ke sath (bacho). Ishaq ne kaha : Aamash ne kaha : Amr-bin-Murra se riwayat hai (kaha ( khaisma se riwayat hai,"
2349,abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur abu-Kuraib donon ne kaha : hamein abu-Muawiya ne Aamash se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne Amr-bin-Murra se unhon-ne khaisma se unhon-ne Hazrat Adii-bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aag ka tazkira farmaya to chehra Mubarak aik taraf modaa aur is mein mubaalgha kiya phir farmaya : aag se bacho . phir rukh Mubarak phera aur door honey ka ishara kiya yahan tak ke hamein guman hua jaisey aap us ( aag ( ki taraf dekh rahe hain phir farmaya : aag se bacho chahey aadhi khajoor ke sath. jisey (ye bhi) na miley to achi baat ke sath . abu-Kuraib ne كانما ( jaisey (ka (lafz) zikr nahi kiya aur kaha : hamein abu-Muawiya ne hadis bayan ki unhon-ne kaha : hamein Aamash ne hadis bayan ki.
2350,"Shoba ne Amr-bin-Murra se pichhli sanad ke sath riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aag ka zikr kiya to us se panah mangi aur teen baar apne chehre-mubarak ke sath door honey ka ishara kiya, phir farmaya : aag se bacho chahey khajoor ke aik tukdey ke zariey se ( bacho ( agar tum (ye bhi) na paogey to achi baat ke sath."
2351,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Aun-bin-abi-Juhaifa se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne munzir-bin-Jareer se aur unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham din ke shuruaati hissey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir they ke aap ke paas kuchh log nangey paon, nangey badan suraakh karke oon ki dhaarii daar chaadrein ya abaaein galley mein daley aur talwaarein latkaey huey aaey unmein se aksar balke sab ke sab Muzar qabeeley se they unki faaqa zadgii ko dekh kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka rukh anwar ghamzada ho gaya aap andar tashrif le gaey phir bahar nikley to Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya unhon-ne azan di aur iqamat kahi aap ne Namaz ada ki, phir khutba diya aur farmaya : aey logo ! ''apne rab se daro jisne tumhen aik jaan se paida kiya.'' padhi. aayat ke aakhir tak be-shak Allah tum par nigraan hai aur wo aayat jo sura hashr mein hai: ''Allah se daro aur har jaan dekhey ke usne kal ke liye aagey kya bheja hai.'' ( phir farmaya ( aadmi par lazim hai ke wo apne Dinar se, apne dirham se, apne kapdey se, apni gandam ke aik saa se, apni khajoor ke aik saa se. yahan tak ke aap ne farmaya : . chahey khajoor ke aik tukdey ke zariey se sadqa karey. (Jareer ne) kaha : to Ansar mein se aik aadmi aik thaili laya uski hatheli us (ko uthaney) se aajiz aaney lagi thi balke aajiz aa gaee thi. kaha : phir log aik doosrey ke peechhey aaney lagey yahan tak ke maine khaney aur kapdon ke do dher dekhey yahan tak ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka chehra Mubarak dekha wo is tarah damak raha tha jaisey is par sona chadhaa hua ho. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jisne Islam mein koi achchha tariqa raaij kiya to uske liye iska ( apna bhi) ajr hai aur unke jaisa ajr bhi jinhoney iske baad us (tareeqey) par amal kiya iske baghair ke unke ajr mein koi kami ho aur jisne Islam mein kisi burey tareeqey ki shuruaat ki iska bojh usi par hai aur unka bojh bhi jinhoney iske baad is par amal kiya iske baghair ke unke bojh mein koi kami ho."
2352,"abu-Usama aur Muaz-Anbari donon ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha mujhey Aun-bin-abi-Juhaifa ne hadis bayan ki unhon-ne kaha : maine munzir-bin-Jareer se suna unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : ham din ke shuruaati hissey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas ( hazir ( they. (aagey) ibne- Jafar ki hadis ki tarah hai. aur ibne- Muaz ki hadis mein izafa hai, kaha : phir aap ne Zohar ki Namaz ada farmai, phir khutba diya."
2353,"abdul-Malik-bin-Umair ne munzir-bin-Jareer se aur unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas betha hua tha ke aap ki khidmat mein aik qaum darmyan mein suraakh karke oon ke dhaarii daar chheethdey galley mein daley aai. padhi. aur pura waqia bayan kiya aur is mein hai : aap ne Zohar ki Namaz padhai , phir aik chhotey se member par tashrif le gaey, Allah Taala ki hamd w sana bayan ki, phir farmaya : bila shubah Allah Taala ne apni kitab mein nazil farmaya hai : aey logo ! ''apne rab se daro.'' aayat ke aakhir tak."
2354,"Abdur-Rehman-bin-Hilaal absa ne Hazrat Jareer-bin-Abdullaah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : badduon mein se kuchh log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey, unke jism par ooni kapdey they, aap ne unki badhaalii dekhi , wo faaqa zada they. phir un (pichhli hadis ke raviyon ( ki hadis ke ham mana riwayat bayan ki."
2355,"Yahya-bin-muaiyan aur Bishr-bin-Khalid ne. lafz Bishr ke hain. hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Muhammad-bin-Jafar (ghandar) ne khabar di, unhon-ne Shoba se, unhon-ne Sulaiman se, unhon-ne abu-Waail se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein sadqa karne ka hukm diya gaya hai, kaha : ham bojh uthaya kartey they. kaha : abu-Aqeel (Raziallahu anhu) ne aadha saa sadqa kiya. aik doosra insan us se zyada koi cheez laya to munaafiqon ne kaha : Allah Taala iske sadqey se ghanii hai aur us doosrey ne mahz dikhlaao kiya hai, is par ye aayate Mubarak utri : ''wo log jo sadqaat ke mamley mein dil khol kar dene waley musalmanon par ta'an kartey hain aur un par bhi jo apni mehnat (ki ujrat (ke siwa kuchh nahi patey.'' Bishr ne ( المطوعين ( (aur baad ke) alfaz nahi kahey ."
2356,"Saeed-bin-Rabe aur Abu-Dawud donon ne Shoba se baqi bachi isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur Saeed-bin-Rabe ki hadis mein hai, kaha : ham apni pushton par bojh uthatey they."
2357,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, wo usey (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tak) pahunchaatey they : sun lo, koi aadmi kisi khandan ko) aisi doodh dene wali) ontni de jo subah ko bada piyala bhar doodh de aur Sham ko bhi bada piyala bhar doodh de to yaqinan us ( ontni (ka ajr bahut bada hai."
2358,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne ( kuchh chizoon se) mana kiya, phir chand khaslaton ka zikr kiya aur Farmaya : jisne doodh peeney ke liye janwar diya to us (ontni , gaaey wghaira) ne sadqey se subah ki aur sadqey se Sham ki, yani apne subah ke doodh se aur apne Sham ke doodh se."
2359,"abu Zinad ne Aaraj se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, neez ibne-Juraij ne kaha : Hasan-bin- Muslim se, unhon-ne Taaus se, unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke kharch karne waley aur sadqa dene waley ki misal us aadmi ki hai jiske jism par chhaatii se lekar hanslii ki haddiyon tak do jubbey ya do zirahein hon. jab kharch karne wala aur doosrey ( rawi ( ne kaha : jab sadqa karne wala. kharch karne ka irada karta hai to wo zirah us (ke jism ( par khul jati hai ya rawaan ho jati hai aur jab kanjoos kharch karne ka irada karta hai to wo us (ke jism ( par sikud jati hai aur har halqa apni jagah (ko mazbootii se) pakad leta hai yahan tak ke us (ki ungliyon (ke poron ko dhanp deta hai aur uske naqsh pa ko mitaa deta hai. kaha : to Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aap ne farmaya : wo ( kanjoos ( usko kholnaa chahta hai lekin wo khultii nahi."
2360,"Ibrahim-bin-Naafe ne Hasan-bin- Muslim se, unhon-ne Taaus se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne misal bayan farmai : kanjoos aur sadqa karne waley ki misal aisey do aadmiyon ki manind (tarah) hai jin (ke jismon ( par lohey ki do zirahein hain. unke donon hath unki chhaatiyon aur hanslii ki haddiyon se jakdey huey hain, to sadqa dene wala jab sadqa dene lagta hai to wo (uski zirah) phail jati hai yahan tak ke uski ungliyon ke poron ko dhanp leti hai aur) zamin par ghaseetney ki wjah se) iske naqsh qadam ko mitaaney lagti hai. aur kanjoos jab sadqa dene ka irada karne lagta hai to wo sikud jati hai aur har halqa apni jagah ko pakad leta hai. ( Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha aap apni ungli garebaan mein daal rahe they, kash! tum Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekhtey ( aisey lagta tha ke) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usey kushaada karna chahtey hain lekin wo kushaada nahi hoti."
2361,"Abdullah-bin-Taaus ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kanjoos aur sadqa dene waley ki misal un do aadmiyon jaisi hai jin par lohey ki do zirahein hain, sadqa dene wala jab sadqa dene ka irada karta hai to wo ( uski zirah ( is par kushaada ho jati hai yahan tak ke iske naqsh pa ko mitaaney lagti hai. aur jab kanjoos sadqa dene ka irada karta hai to wo ( zirah ( is par sikud jati hai aur uske donon hath uski hanslii ke sath jakad jatey hain aur har halqa sath waley halqey ke sath pewast ho jata hai. (abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : wo koshish karta hai ke usey kushaada karey lekin nahi kar sakta."
2362,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik aadmi ne kaha : main aaj raat zaroor kuchh sadqa karunga to wo apna sadqa lekar nikla aur usey aik zaaniya ke hath mein de diya, subah ko log baatein karne lagey ke aaj raat aik zaaniya par sadqa kiya gaya, us aadmi ne kaha : aey Allah teri hamd ! zaaniya par) sadqa hua) mein zaroor sadqa karunga, phir wo sadqa lekar nikla to usey aik maaldaar ke hath mein de diya. subah ko log baatein karne lagey : aik maal daar par sadqa kiya gaya. usne kaha : aey Allah teri hamd ! maaldaar par (sadqa hua) mein zaroor kuchh sadqa karunga aur wo apna sadqa lekar nikla to usey aik chor ke hath par rakh diya. log subah ko baatein karne lagey : chor par sadqa kiya gaya. to usne kaha : aey Allah ! sab hamd terey hi liye hai, zaaniya par, maaldaar par, aur chor par (sadqa hua) . usko ( khuwab mein) kaha gaya tumhara sadqa qabool ho chuka, jahan tak zaaniya ka talluq hai to ho sakta hai ke us ( sadqey ( ki wjah se zaaniya apne zina se paak daamanii ikhtiyar kar ley aur shayad maal daar ibrat pakdey aur Allah ne jo usey diya hai) khud ( usmein sadqa karey aur shayad uski wjah se chor apni chori se baaz aa jaey."
2363,"Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : be-shak aik musalman amanat daar khaazin ( khazaanchii ( jo diye gaey hukm par amal karta hai. (ya farmaya : ada karta hai) usey khush dillii ke sath poorey ka pura ( balke) waafir , us shakhs ko ada kar deta hai jiske barey mein usey hukm diya gaya hai to wo ( khaazin bhi) . . do sadqa karne walon mein se aik hai."
2364,"Jarir ne Mansoor se, unhon-ne Shaqiq se, unhon-ne Masruq se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab aurat ujaadey baghair apne ghar ke khaney se kharch karti hai to usey kharch karne ki wjah se ajr milega aur uske khawind ko iske kamaaney ki wjah se apna ajr milega aur khazaanchii ke liye bhi isi tarah ( ajr ( hai. ye aik doosrey ke ajr mein koi kami nahi kartey."
2365,Fuzail-bin-ayaaz ne Mansoor se isi sanad ke sath (pichhli hadis ki tarah ( riwayat ki aur unhon-ne (apne ghar ke khaney mein se ke bajaey) (apne khawind ke khaney mein se) ke alfaz kahey .
2366,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne kaha : abu-Muawiya ne hamein Aamash se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Shaqiq se, unhon-ne Masruq se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab aurat ujaadey baghair apne khawind ke ghar se ( Allah ki raah mein) kharch karti hai to uske liye iska ajr hai aur us ( khawind (ke liye bhi iske kamaaney ki wjah se waisaa hi ajr hai aur us aurat ke liye iske kharch karne ki wjah se. aur khazaanchii ke liye bhi us jaisa ( ajr ( hai, un (sab logon (ke ajr mein kuchh kami kiye baghair ."
2367,ibne-Numair ne kaha : hamein mere walid aur abu-Muawiya ne Aamash se usi (uper zikr ki gaee) sanad ke sath isi tarah hadis bayan ki.
2368,"Muhammad-bin-Zaid ne abul-laham (Ghifari) (Raziallahu anhu) ke aazad karda ghulam Umer (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : main ghulam tha, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha : kya main apne malikon ke maal mein se kuchh sadqa kar sakta hoon? aap ne farmaya : haan , aur ajr tum donon ke darmyan aadha-aadhaa (barabar-barabar) hoga."
2369,"Yazeed-bin-abi-Ubaid ne kaha : maine abul-laham (Raziallahu anhu) ke aazad karda ghulam Umer (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey mere aaqa ne gosht ke tukdey karke khushk karne ka hukm diya, mere paas aik miskeen aa gaya to maine usmein se kuchh khila diya. mere aaqa ko iska pata chal gaya. to unhon-ne mujhey maara. is par main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye baat batai . aap ne usey bula kar puchha : tum ne usey kyon maara? usne kaha : mere hukm ke baghair mera khana (doosron ko) deta hai. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ajr tum donon ke darmyan hoga. (tum donon ko milega)"
2370,"Hammam-bin-Munabbah se riwayat hai, kaha : ye wo hadisein hain jo Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein Muhammad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kin, phir unhon-ne kuchh hadisey zikr kin, unmein se ye bhi thi ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aurat apne khawind ki maujoodgii main ( nafli ( roza na rakhey, magar jab uski ijazat ho. aur uske ghar mein uski maujoodgii mein (apne kisi mohrim (ehraam walaa shakhs) ko bhi) uski ijazat ke baghair na aaney de aur us ( aurat ( ne uske hukm ke baghair uski kamaaii se jo kuchh kharch kiya to yaqinan iska aadha ajr us ( khawind (ke liye hai."
2371,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Humaid-bin-Abdur-Rehman se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne Allah ki raah mein do-do cheezein kharch kiin usey jannat mein awaz di jaeygi ke aey Allah ke bandey ! ye ( darwaza ( bahut achchha hai. (kyonke wo doosrey mein se janey ka haqdaar bhi hoga ( jo Namaz padhney walon mein se hoga, usey Namaz ke darwazey se pukara jaeyga, jo jihad karne walon mein se hoga, usey jihad ke darwazey se pukara jaeyga, jo sadqa diye walon mein se hoga, usey sadqey waley darwazey se pukara jaeyga, aur jo roza daaron mein se hoga, usey baab rayyan (sairaabii ke darwazey) se pukara jaeyga Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! kisi insan ko un tamam darwazon se pukaarey janey ki zarurat to nahi hai lekin kya koi aisa bhi) khush naseeb ( hoga jisey un tamam darwazon se bulaya jaeyga ? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : haan , aur mujhey ummeed hai tum unhi mein se hongey."
2372,Saleh aur Mamar donon ne Zohri se Yunus ki uper zikr ki gaee sanad ke sath usi ki hadis ke ham mana hadis bayan ki.
2373,"abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne Allah ki raah mein joda-jodaa kharch kiya, usey jannat ke pahrey-daar bulaaengey, darwazey ke tamam pahrey-daar ( kahengey:) aey falan ! aa jao . is par Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! aisey fard ko kisi qism (ke nuqsan) ka andesha nahi hoga. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mujhey ummeed hai ke tum unhi mein se hogey ."
2374,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aaj tum mein se rozey daar kon hai? Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aaj tum mein se janazey ke sath kon gaya? Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main. aap ne puchha : aaj tum mein se kisi ne kisi miskeen ko khana khilaaya hai? Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya : maine. aap ne puchha : to aaj tum mein se kisi bimar ki timar daari kis ne ki? Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kisi insan mein ye nekiyan jama nahi hotiin magar wo yaqinan jannat mein dakhil hota hai."
2375,"Hafs-bin-ghayaas ne Hisham se, unhon-ne Fatima-binte-munzir se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Asma-binte-abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon kaha : ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : (maal ko) kharch . ya har taraf phailaao ya (pani ki tarah) bahaao . padhi. aur gino nahi warna Allah bhi tumhen gin-gin kar dega."
2376,"Muhammad-bin-khaazim ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Hisham-bin-Urwa ne Ibad-bin-Hamza aur Fatima-binte-munzir se hadis bayan ki aur unhon-ne Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : (maal ko) har taraf kharch karo. padhi. ya (pani ki tarah bahaao ya kharch karo. padhi. aur shumaar na karo warna Allah bhi tumhen shumaar kar-karke dega aur sanbhaal kar na rakho warna Allah bhi tum se sanbhaal kar rakhega ."
2377,"Muhammad-bin-Bishr ne kaha : hamein Hisham ne Ibad-bin-Hamza se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Asma (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse kaha,.... padhi. un (uper zikr ki gaee rawiyon) ki hadis ki tarah."
2378,"Ibad-bin-Abdullah-bin-Zubair ne khabar di ke unhon-ne Hazrat Asma-binte-abi-Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin aur arz kiya, aey Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! jo kuchh Zuber mujhey de iske siwa mere paas koi cheez nahi hoti to kya mujh par koi gunah to nahi ke jo wo mujhey de usmein se thoda sa sadqa kar dun? aap ne farmaya : apni taaqat ke mutabiq, thoda bhi kharch karo aur bartan mein sanbhaal kar na rakho warna Allah Taala bhi tum se sanbhaal kar rakhega ."
2379,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmaya kartey they : aey musalman aurton ! koi padausan apni padausan ke liye ( tohfey ko) haqeer na samjhey chahey wo bakri ka aik khur ho. (jo muyassar hai bhej do.)
2380,Ubaidullah se riwayat hai kaha : mujhey Khubaib-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne Hafs-bin-Aasim se khabar di unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : saat (7) qism ke logon ko Allah Taala us din apne saaey mein saaya muhaiya karega jis din uske saaey ke siwa koi saaya nahi hoga. adl karne wala hukmaraan aur wo naujawaan jo Allah ki ibadat ke sath parwaan chadhaa aur wo aadmi jiska dil masjid mein atkaa hua hai aur aisey do aadmi jinhoney Allah ki khaatir aik doosrey se mohabbat ki usi par ikatthey huey aur usi par juda huey aur aisa aadmi jisey martabey aur Husn wali aurat ne (gunah ki) dawat di to us ( aadmi ( ne kaha : main Allah se darta hun aur wo aadmi jisne chipa kar sadqa kiya yahan tak ke iska baayan hath jo kuchh kharch kar raha hai usey dayan nahi janta aur wo aadmi jisne tanhai mein Allah ko yad kiya to uski aankhen bahney lagein.
2381,"Imam Malik ne Khubaib-bin-Abdur-Rehman se unhon-ne Hafs-bin-Aasim se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) . ya Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) . se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, padhi. ( aagey ( jis tarah Ubaidullah ki hadis hai aur unhon-ne (aisa aadmi jiska dil masjid mein atkaa hua hai ke bajaey) kaha : (رجل معلق بالمسجد اذا خرج منه حتي يعود اليه ) ''wo aadmi jab masjid se nikalta hai to usi ke sath muallaq rehta hai yahan tak ke usmein lot aaey.''"
2382,"Jarir ne Ammara-bin-Qaqa se unhon-ne abu-Zura se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : aik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! kon sa sadqa ( ajr mein) bada hai? aap ne farmaya : tum (us waqt) sadqa karo jab tum tandurust ho aur maal ki khahish rakhtey ho ghurbat se dartey ho aur tawangarii ki ummeed rakhtey ho aur is qadr taakheer na karo ke jab ( tumhari jaan ( halaq tak pahunch jaey ( phir ( tum kaho : itna falan ka hai aur itna falan kaa. ab to wo falan ( waaris (ka ho hi chuka hai."
2383,"ibne- Fuzel ne Umara se unhon-ne abu-Zura se unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : aik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! kon sa sadqa ajr mein bada hai? aap ne farmaya : haan tumharey bap ka bhala ho tumhen is baat se aagaah kiya jaeyga, wo ye ke tum us waqt sadqa karo jab tum tandurust ho aur maal ki khahish rakhtey ho faqr se dartey ho aur lambi zindagi ki ummeed rakhtey ho aur) khud ko) is qadr mohlat na do ke jab tumhari jaan halaq tak pahunch jaey to phir ( wasiiyat kartey huey) kaho falan ka itna hai aur falan ka itna hai wo to falan ka ho hi chuka ."
2384,abdul-Wahid ne kaha : ham se Ammara-bin-Qaqa ne ( baqi bachi ( isi sanad ke sath Jarir ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki albatta kaha : kon sa sadqa afzal hai?
2385,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jabke aap member par they aur sadqe aur sawal se bchney ka zikr kar rahe they : uper wala hath, nichey waley hath se behtar hai aur uper wala hath kharch karne wala hai aur nichey wala maangney wala hai."
2386,Hazrat Hakeem-bin-Hizaam (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : sabse afzal sadqa . ya sabse achchha sadqa . padhi. wo hai jiske peechhey (dil ki) tanvgarii ho aur uper wala hath nichey waley hath se behtar hai aur) dene ki) shuruaat us se karo jiski tum kafalet kartey ho.
2387,"Hazrat Hakeem-bin-Hizaam (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai unhon-ne kaha maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se  maangaa to aap ne mujhey ata farmaya. maine ( dobara ( maanga to aap ne mujhey de diya. maine phir aap se sawal kiya to aap ne mujhey diya, phir farmaya : ye maal shaadaab ( aankhon ko lubhaa ne wala (aur sheereen hai. jo to usey laalich w tamaa (lalach) ke baghair lega uske liye usmein barkat ata ki jaeygi. aur jo dil ke laalich se lega , uske liye usmein barkat nahi dali jaeygi. wo us insan ki tarah hoga jo khata hai lekin sair nahi hota aur uper wala hath nichey waley hath se behtar hai."
2388,"Hazrat abu-Amama (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Adam ke betey ! be-shak to ( zarurat ( se zayed maal kharch kar de, ye terey liye behtar hai aur to usey roke rakhey to ye terey liye bura hai. aur guzar Basar jitna rakhney par tumhen koi malaamat nahi ki jaeygi aur kharch ki shuruat unse karo jinke (kharch ke) tum zimme-daar ho, aur uper wala hath nichey waley hath se behtar hai."
2389,Abdullah-bin-Aamir yehsubi ne kaha maine Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna : tum us hadis ke siwa jo Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke daur mein) bayan ki jati ( thi dusri hadisein bayan karne se bacho. kyonke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) logon ko) riwayat ke silsiley mein bhi) Allah ka khof dilaya kartey they. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna aap farma rahe they Allah Taala jiske sath bhalai karna chahta hai usey Deen mein gehra faham (samajh) ata farma deta hai. aur maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey bhi suna : main to bas khazaanchii hon jis ko main khush dillii se dun uske liye usmein barkat daal di jaeygi aur jis ko main maangney par aur (uske ( laalich ke sabab se dun uski haalat us insan jaisi hogi jo khata hai aur sair nahi hota.
2390,Muhammad-bin-Abdullah-bin-Numair ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne Amr (bin-Dinar ( se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne Wahab-bin-Munabba se unhon-ne apne bhai Hammam se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : maangney mein israar na karo Allah ki qism ! aisa nahi ho sakta ke tum mein se koi shakhs mujh se kuchh maangey mein usey na-pasand karta hun. phir bhi uska sawal mujh se kuchh nikalwaa ley to jo main usko dun usmein barkat ho.
2391,ibne-abi-Umar Makki ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne Amr-bin-Dinar se hadis sunai kaha : mujhey Wahab-bin-Munabbah ne. padhi. jab main san'aa mein unke paas unke ghar gaya aur unhon-ne mujhey apne ghar ke darakht se akhrot khilay. apne bhai se hadis bayan ki. unhon-ne kaha : maine Muawiya-bin-abi-Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna aap farma rahe they. ( aagey ( usi (pichhli ( hadis ke mutabiq bayan kiya.
2392,Humaid-bin-Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf ne kaha : maine Hazrat Muawiya-bin-abi-Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo khutba detey huey keh rahe they : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna aap farma rahe they : Allah jiske sath bhalai ka irada farmata hai usey Deen ka gehra faham (samajh) ata farma deta hai aur main to bas taqseem karne wala hun aur deta Allah hai.
2393,"Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : (asl) miskeen ye ghoomney wala nahi jo logon ke paas chakkar lagata hai phir aik do luqmey ya aik do khajoorey usey wapas lota deti hain. (sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen)) ne puchha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! to miskeen kon hai? aap ne farmaya : jo itni tawangarii nahi paata jo usey (sawal se) mustaghni kar de, na hi us (ke zarurat mand honey) ka pata chalta hai ke usko sadqa diya jaey aur na hi wo logon se koi cheez mangta hai."
2394,"Ismail ne jo ibne- Jafar (bin-abi-kaseer ( hain, kaha : mujhey Sharik ne Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke aazad karda ghulam Ata-bin-Yasar se khabar di, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : (asl) miskeen wo nahi jisey aik do khajoorein ya aik do luqmey lota detey hain. asl miskeen sawal se bchney wala hai, chaho to ye aayat padh lo : ''wo logon se chimat kar (israar se) nahi maangtey.''"
2395,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar (bin-abi-kaseer) ne kaha : mujhey Sharik ne khabar di, kaha : mujhey Ata-bin-Yasar aur Abdur-Rehman-bin-abi-Umra ne bataya ke un donon ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, padhi. ( aagey Muhammad ke bhai ( Ismail ki riwayat ki tarah hai."
2396,"Abdul-Aala-bin-Abdul-Aala ne Mamar se, unhon-ne (Imam Zohri ke bhai ( Abdullah-bin-Muslim se, unhon-ne Hamza-bin-Abdullah (bin-Umar) se aur unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se kisi shakhs ke sath sawal chimtaa rehta hai yahan tak ke wo Allah se milega to uske chehrey par gosht ka aik tukda bhi na hoga."
2397,Ismail-bin-Ibrahim ne Mamar se isi sanad ke sath yahi riwayat bayan ki aur us main ( gosht ke) tukdey ke alfaz nahi hain.
2398,Ubaidullah-bin-abi-Jafar ne Hamza-bin-Abdullah-bin-Umar se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne apne walid ko ye kehtey huey suna : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aadmi logon se sawal karta rehta hai) maangna uski aadat bin jata hai) yahan tak ke wo qiyamat ke din us haalat mein aayega ke uske chehrey par gosht ka aik tukda bhi na hoga.
2399,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo shakhs maal badhaney ke liye logon se unka maal mangta hai wo aag ke angaarey mangta hai, kam (ikatthey) kar ley ya zyada kar ley."
2400,"bayan-bin-abi-Bishr ne Qais-bin-abi-Hazim se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : tum mein se koi shakhs subah ko nikley apni pusht par lakdiyan ikatthi kar laey aur us se sadqa karey aur logon (ke atiyon) se be niyaaz ho jaey, wo us se behtar hai ke kisi aadmi se maangey , wo (chahey to) usey de ya (chahey to) mahroom rakhey, bila shubah uper wala hath nichey waley hath se afzal hai aur (kharch karne ki) shuruaat unse karo jinki tum kifaalat kartey ho."
2401,"Ismail ne kaha : mujhey Qais-bin-abi-Hazim ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : ham Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas hazir huey to unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah ki qism ! tum mein se aik subah ko nikley, apni peeth par lakdiyan laey aur unhein bechey . phir bayan ki hadis ki tarah hadis sunai."
2402,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ke aazad karda ghulam abu-Ubaid se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi iindhan ka gathaa baandhey aur apni peeth par laadey, aur bech de, uske liye us se behtar hai ke kisi aadmi se sawal karey, (chahey) wo usey de ya na de."
2403,"abu-Muslim-Kholani se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : mujh se aik piyarey amanat daar (shakhs) ne hadis bayan ki wo aisa hai ke mujhey pyara bhi hai aur wo aisa hai ke mere nazdeek amanat daar bhi hai. yani Hazrat Auf-bin-Malik Ashjai (Raziallahu anhu)..... . unhon-ne kaha : ham nau (9) , aath (8) ya saat (7) aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney (hazir) they, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya tum Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bait nahi karogey? aur ham ne abhi nai-nai bait ki thi. to ham ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! ham aap se bait kar chukey hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum Allah ke rasool se bait nahi karogey? ham ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! ham aap se bait kar chukey hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir farmaya : tum Allah ke rasool se bait nahi karogey? to ham ne apne hath badha diye aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! ham (eik baar) aap se bait kar chukey hain, ab kis baat par aap se bait karein? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : is baat par ke tum Allah ki ibadat karogey aur uske sath kisi cheez ko Sharik nahi thehrao gey aur panch namazon par, aur is baat par ke itaat karogey aur aik jumla aahista se farmaya aur logon se kisi cheez ka sawal na karogey. iske baad maine unmein se kuchh afraad ko dekha ke unmein se kisi ka kodaa gir jata to kisi se na kehta ke utha kar uske hath mein de dey ."
2404,"Hazrat qabeesa-bin-makhaariq-hilaalii (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : maine (logon ke maamlaat mein islaah ke liye) adaaeygi ki aik zimme-dari qabool ki aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua ke aap se uske liye kuchh maangon to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : thehro yahan tak ke hamarey paas sadqa aa jaey to ham wo tumhen de dene ka hukm dein. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey Qabisa ! teen qism ke afraad mein se kisi aik ke siwa aur kisi ke liye sawal karna jaaiz nahi : aik wo aadmi jisne kisi badi adaaeygi ki zimme-dari qabool kar li, uske liye us waqt tak sawal karna halal ho jata hai yahan tak ke usko hasil kar ley, uske baad (sawal se) ruk jaey, doosra wo aadmi jis par koi aafat aa padi ho jisne uska maal tabah kar diya ho, uske liye sawal karna halal ho jata hai yahan tak ke wo zindagi ki guzraan durust kar ley. ya farmaya : zindagi ki baqaa ka saman kar ley. aur tesraa wo aadmi jo faaqey ka shikar ho gaya, yahan tak ke uski qaum ke teen aqlmand afraad khadey ho jayen (aur keh dein (ke falan aadmi faaqa zada ho gaya hai to uske liye bhi maangna halal ho gaya yahan tak ke wo durust guzraan hasil kar ley. .......۔ . ya farmaya : zindagi baqi rakhney jitna hasil kar ley. ......۔ . aey Qabisa ! in Suraton ke siwa sawal karna haram hai aur sawal karne wala haram khata hai."
2405,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Saalim-bin-Abdullah-bin-Umar se aur unhon-ne apne walid ( Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Umar-bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kabhi mujhey inayat farmatey they, to main arz karta : kisi aisey aadmi ko inayat farma dijiye jo iska mujh se zyada zarurat mand ho yahan tak ke aik baar aap ne mujhey bahut Sara maal ata kar diya to maine kaha : kisi aisey fard ko ata kar dijiye jo iska mujh se zyada mohtaaj ho. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : usey ley lo aur aisa jo maal tumharey paas is tarah aaey ke na to tum iske khahish mand ho aur na hi maangney waley ho to usko ley lo aur jo maal is tarah na miley uska khayal bhi dil mein na laao."
2406,"Amr-bin-Haris ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Salim se aur unhon-ne apne walid Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Hazrat Umar-bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ko Atiya detey to umr (Raziallahu anhu) arz kartey : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! ye mujh se zyada zarurat mand shakhs ko de dijiye. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : usko ley lo aur apna maal bana lo ya usey sadqa kar do aur us maal mein se jo tumharey paas is tarah aaey ke tum na uske khahish mand ho na maangney waley to usko ley lo aur jo (maal ( is tarah na miley to uska khayal bhi dil mein na laao. Salim ne kaha : usi wjah se Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bhi kisi se kuchh nahi maangtey they aur jo cheez unhein pesh ki jati thi usko radd nahi kartey they."
2407,"saaib-bin-Yazeed ne Abdullah-bin-sa'dii se, unhon-ne Hazrat Umar-bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se (usi ki tarah) hadis bayan ki."
2408,"Leis ne Bukair se, unhon-ne Basar-bin-Saeed se aur unhon-ne ibne- Saaidi maalikii se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Hazrat Umar-bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne sadqey (ki wsoolii (ke liye aamil muqarrar kiya, jab main us kaam se farigh hua aur unhein (wsool karda) maal la kar ada kar diya, to unhon-ne mujhey kaam ki ujrat dene ka hukm diya. maine kaha : maine to ye kaam mahz Allah ki (raza ki) khaatir kiya hai aur mera ajr Allah ne dena hai. to unhon-ne kaha : jo tumhen diya jaey usey ley lo kyonke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahade-mubaarak mein kaam kiya tha, aap ne mujhey mere kaam ki mazdoorii di to maine bhi tumhari jaisi baat kahi to mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tumhen tumharey maangey baghair koi cheez di jaey to khaao aur sadqa karo."
2409,"Amr-bin-Haris ne Bukair-bin-Ashajj se, unhon-ne Basar-bin-Saeed se aur unhon-ne ibne- sa'dii se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Hazrat Umar-bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne sadqa wsool karne ke liye aamil banaya. padhi. ( aagey ( Leis ki hadis ki tarah (riwaayat bayan ki.)"
2410,"Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne usey Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tak marfoo bayan kiya, aap ne farmaya : boodhey aadmi ka dil do chizon ki mohabbat mein jawan hota hai : zindagi ki mohabbat aur maal ki."
2411,Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : do chizon ki mohabbat mein boodhey ka dil bhi jawan rehta hai : zindagi lambi honey aur maal ki mohabbat mein.
2412,"abu-Awana ne Qatada se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Adam ka betaa boodha ho jata hai magar uski do cheezein jawan rehti hain : daulat ki hirs aur umr ki hirs (laalich)."
2413,"Muaz-bin-Hisham ke walid Hisham ne Qatada se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, padhi. ( aagey ( isi tarah hai."
2414,"Shoba ne kaha : maine Qatada se suna, wo Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan kar rahe they, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki. ( aagey ( isi tarah hai."
2415,"abu-Awana ne Qatada se unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar Adam ke betey ke paas maal ki) bhari hui ( do wadiyan hon to wo teesri hasil karna chaahega aadmi ka pet mitti ke siwa koi aur cheez nahi bhar sakti aur Allah usi ki taraf tawajjoh farmata hai jo (uski taraf) tawajjoh karta hai."
2416,"Shoba ne kaha : maine Qatada se suna, wo Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kar rahe they kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna farma rahe they mujhey pata nahi hai ke ye alfaz aap par nazil huey they ya aap (khud hi) farma rahe they. (aagey) abu-Awana ki hadis ki tarah hai."
2417,"ibne-Shahab ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : agar ibne-Aadam ke paas soney ki (bhari hui) aik wadi ho to wo chaahega ke uske paas aik aur wadi ho, iska munh mitti ke siwa koi aur cheez nahi bhartii Allah uski taraf tawajjoh farmata hai jo Allah ki taraf tawajjoh karta hai."
2418,"mujhey Zuhair-bin-Harab aur Haron-bin-Abdullah ne hadis sunai donon ne kaha : hamein Hajjaj-bin-Muhammad ne ibne-Juraij se hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Ata se suna keh rahe they maine Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : agar Adam ke betey ke paas maal se bhari hui aik wadi ho to wo chaahega ke uske paas us jaisi aur wadi bhi ho. aadmi ke dil ko mitti ke siwa kuchh aur nahi bhar sakta aur Allah is par tawajjoh farmata hai jo uski taraf mutwajjeh ho, Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha mujhey malum nahi ye Quran mein se hai ya nahi. aur Zuhair ki riwayat mein hai unhon-ne kaha : mujhey malum nahi ye baat Quran mein se hai) ya nahi ( unhon-ne Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ka zikr nahi kiya."
2419,"abu-harab-bin-abi-Aswad ke walid se riwayat hai unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) ne ahal Basra ke qaariyon ki taraf (unhein bulane ke liye qaasid ( bheja to unke yahaan teen so aadmi aaey jo Quran padh chukey they, to unhon ( abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha : tum ahal Basra ke behtreen log aur unke qaari ho uski tilawat kartey raha karo, tum par lambi muddat (ka waqfa ( na guzrey ke tumharey dil sakht ho jayen jis tarah unke dil sakht ho gaey they jo tum se pahley they. ham aik sura padha kartey they jisey ham lambai aur) darane ki) shiddat mein (sura ( baraah se tashbeeh diya kartey to wo mujhey bhulaa di gaee iske siwa ke iska ye tukda mujhey yad reh gaya. ''agar Adam ke betey ke paas maal ki do wadiyan hon to wo teesri wadi ka mutlaa shai hoga aur ibne-Aadam ka pet to mitti ke siwa koi cheez nahi bhartii.'' ham aik aur sura padha kartey they jis ko ham tasbeeh wali Suraton mein se aik sura se tashbeeh diya kartey they wo bhi mujhey bhulaa di gaee haan usmein se mujhey ye yad hai. ''aey eman waalo! wo baat kehtey kyon ho jo kartey nahi wo bataur shahadat tumhari gardanon mein likh di jaeygi aur qiyamat ke din tum se iske barey mein sawal kiya jaeyga.''"
2420,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ghinaa (maaldaari) maal w asbaab ki kasarat se nahi balke haqiqi ghinaa dil ki be-nayaazi hai.
2421,"ayaaz-bin-Abdullah-bin-Sad se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo keh rahe they Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khadey ho kar logon ko khutba diya aur farmaya : nahi Allah ki qism ! logo ! mujhey tumharey barey mein kisi cheez ka dar nahi siwaey duniya ki us zeenat ke jo Allah Taala tumharey liye zahir karega. aik aadmi kehney laga. aey Allah ke rasool! kiya khair shar ko ley aaeygi? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghadi bhar khamosh rahe phir farmaya : tum ne kis tarah kaha? usne kaha Allah ke rasool! maine kaha thi kiya khair shar ko laey gii? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se kaha : khair khair hi ko laatii hai lekin kiya wo (duniya ki zeb w zeenat apney aap mein) khair hai? wo sab kuchh jo bahaar ugati hai) janwar ko) uphaarey se mar daalta hai ya maut ke qareeb kar deta hai. aisey sabza khaney waley janwar ke siwa jisne khaya aur jab uski ko-kheen bhar gain (wo sair ho gaya) to ( mazeed khaney ke bajaey) us ne suraj ka rukh kar liya aur baith kar goubar ya peshab kiya. phir jugaalii ki aur dobara khaya to (usi tarah) jo insan us (maal (ke haq ke mutabiq maal leta hai, uske liye usmein barkat daal di jati hai aur jo insan iske haq ke baghair maal leta hai wo uski tarah hai jo khata hai lekin sair nahi hota."
2422,"Zaid-bin-Aslam ne Ata-bin-Yasar se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mujhey tumharey barey mein sabse zyada dar duniya ki us shadabi aur zeenat se hai jo Allah Taala tumharey liye zahir karega . sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) ne kaha duniya ki shaadaabii aur zeenat kiya hai? aap ne farmaya : zamin ki barkat. unhon-ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! kya khair shar ko ley aati hai? aap ne farmaya : khair siwaey khair ke kuchh nahi laatii , khair siwaey khair ke kuchh nahi laatii , khair siwaey khair ke kuchh nahi laatii , wo sab kuchh jo bahaar ugati hai wo ( zyada khaney ki wjah se honey wali bad hazamii ka sabab bin kar) mar deta hai ya maut ke qareeb kar deta hai siwaey us chaara khaney waley janwar ke jo khata hai yahan tak ke jab uski donon ko-kheen phool jati hain (wo sair ho jata hai) to wo ( mazeed khana chhod kar) suraj ki taraf munh kar leta hai, phir jugaalii karta hai, peshab karta hai, goubar karta hai, phir laut'taa hai aur khata hai, bila shubah ye maal shaadaab aur sheereen hai jisne usey uske haq ke mutabiq liya aur haq (ke musrif ( hi mein kharch kiya to wo (maal ( bahut hi muaawin w madadgaar hoga aur jisne usey haq ke baghair liya wo us insan ki tarah hoga jo khata hai lekin sair nahi hota."
2423,"Hilaal-bin-abi-Memuna ne Ata-bin-Yasar se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) member par tashrif farma huey aur ham aap ke ird-gird baith gaey to aap ne farmaya : mujhey apne baad tumharey barey mein jis cheez ka khof hai wo duniya ki shadabi aur zeenat hai jiske darwazey tum par khol diye jaengey. to aik aadmi ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! kiya khair shar ko ley aaeygi? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) iske jawab main ( kuchh der ( khamosh rahe us se kaha gaya : tera kiya mamla hai? tum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se baat kartey ho ( jabke ( wo tum se baat nahi kar rahe ? kaha : aur ham ne dekha ke aap par wahi utari ja rahi hai phir aap paseena po nchhtey huey apne mamool (routine) ki haalat mein aagey aur farmaya : ye sawal karne wala kahan se aaya? . goya aap ne uski tahseen farmai . phir farmaya : waqia ye hai ke khair shar ko nahi laatii. aur bila shubah mausam bahaar jo ugaa ta hai wo (apni shadabi aur marghoobiyat ki bina par) mar deta hai ya maut ke qareeb kar deta hai siwaey sabza khaaney waley us haiwaan ke jisne khaya yahan tak ke jab uski ko-kheen bhar gain to usne suraj ki aankh ki taraf munh kar liya (aur aaraam se baith kar khaya hua Hazam kiya) phir leed ki, peshab kiya iske baad) phir se) ghaas khaaii. yaqinan ye maal shaadaab aur shareen hai aur ye us musalman ka behtreen sathi hai, jisne usmein se miskeen, yateem aur musaafir ko diya...... padhi. ya jo alfaz Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaai . padhi. aur haqiqat ye hai jo usey uske haq ke baghair leta hai wo us aadmi ki tarah hai jo khata hai aur sair nahi hota aur qiyamat ke din wo (maal ( uske khilaf gawah hoga."
2424,"imam Malik-bin-Anas ne ibne-Shahab Zohri se, unhon-ne Ata-bin-Yazeed Lesi se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Ansar ke kuchh logon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se maal ka sawal kiya. aap ne unko de diya, unhon-ne phir maanga , aap ne de diya yahan tak ke aap ke paas jo kuchh tha wo khatm ho gaya to aap ne farmaya : mere paas jo bhi maal hoga main usey hargiz tum se (bacha kar) zakheera na karunga (tumhii mein baant doonga), jo shakhs sawal se bchney ki koshish karega Allah usey bachaaey ga aur jo istighnaa (be niyaazii) ikhtiyar karega Allah usko be niyaaz kar dega aur jo sabr karega (sawal se baaz rahega) Allah Taala usko sabr (ki quwwat ( inayat farmaeyga aur kisi ko aisa koi Atiya nahi diya gaya jo sabr se behtar aur wasee tar ho."
2425,Mamar ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath isi tarah riwayat ki.
2426,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wo insan kaamyaab w baa-muraad ho gaya jo musalman ho gaya, aur usey guzar Basar ke baqadr rozii mili , aur Allah Taala ne usey jo diya is par qanaa'at ki toufeeq bakhshii."
2427,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya (dua farmai ( : aey Allah ! aale Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki rozii kam se kam khaney jitni kar de.
2428,Hazrat Umar-bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kuchh maal taqseem kiya to maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! Allah ki qism ! unke ilawa (jinhein aap ne ata farmaya ( doosrey log iske zyada haqdaar they. aap ne farmaya : unhon-ne mujhey aik cheez ikhtiyar karne par majbur kar diya ke ya to ye mazmoom tareeqey ( be-jaa israar ( se sawal karein ya mujhey kanjoos bana dein to main kanjoos banney wala nahi hun.
2429,"imam Malik-bin-Anas ne Ishaq-bin-Abdullah-bin-abi-Talha se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha, main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath chal raha tha aap (ke kandhon ( par khaasey motey kinarey ki aik najraanii chadar thi itney mein aik badwi aap ke paas aa gaya aur aap ki chadar se (pakad kar) aapko zor se khinchaa. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki gardan ki aik taraf ki taraf nazar ki jis par iske zor se khinchney ke baais chadar ke kinarey ne gehra nishan daal diya tha phir usne kaha : aey Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! Allah ka jo maal aap ke paas hai is mein se mujhey bhi dene ka hukm dein to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uski taraf mutwajjeh huey hans padey aur usey kuchh dene ka hukm diya."
2430,Hammam Ikrima-bin-Ammar aur Auzai sab ne Ishaq-bin-Abdullah-bin-abi-Talha se unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se yahi hadis riwayat ki. Ikrima-bin-Ammar ki hadis mein ye izafa hai phir us ne aapko zor se apni taraf khinchaa to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us badwi ke seeney se ja takraaey aur Hammam ki hadis mein hai us ne aap ke sath kheenchaa taanii shuru kar di yahan tak ke chadar phat gaee aur yahan tak ke iska kinaaraa Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki gardan Mubarak mein reh gaya.
2431,Leis ne ( Abdullah )-bin-abi-mulaika se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Miswar-bin-Makhrama (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qubaaein (chaaderey) taqseem kiin aur Makhrima (Raziallahu anhu) ko koi cheez na di to Makhrima (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : mere betey ! mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas ley jao to main unke sath gaya unhon-ne kaha : andar jao aur meri khaatir aapko bula lao maine unki khaatir aapko bulaya to aap is tarah uski taraf aaey ke aap (ke kandhey ( par un (chaadron) mein se aik Quba thi aap ne farmaya : ye maine tumharey liye chipa kar rakhi thi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uski taraf nazar utha kar farmaya : Makhrima razi ho gaya.
2432,"Ayub sakhtiyan ne Abdullah-bin-Ubai-mulaika se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Miswar-bin-Makhrama (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas qubaaein (chaaderey) aaein to mujhey mere walid Makhrima (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha mujhey aap ke paas ley chalo ummeed hai aap hamein bhi unmein se (koii Quba ( inayat farmaaengey . mere walid ne darwazey par khadey ho kar guftgu ki to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unki awaz pehchan li. aap bahar nikley to Quba aap ke sath thi aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unhein uski khubiyan dikhaa rahe they aur farma rahe they : maine ye tumharey liye chipa kar rakhi thi, maine tumharey liye chipa kar rakhi thi."
2433,Hasan-bin-Ali-Hulwani aur abd-bin-Humaid ne kaha : hamein Yaqoob-bin-Ibrahim-bin-Sad ne hadis sunai kaha mere walid ne hamein Saleh se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Aamir-bin-Sad ne apne walid Hazrat Sad (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kuchh logon ko maal diya jabke mein bhi unmein betha hua tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unmein se aik aadmi ko chhod diya usko na diya. wo mere liye un sab ki nisbat zyada pasandida tha main uth kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas gaya aur raazdaarii ke sath aap se kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! kya wjah hai aap falan se ea'raaz farma rahe hain? Allah ki qism ! main to usey momin samajhta hun aap ne farmaya : ya musalman. main kuchh der ke liye chup raha phir jo main uske barey mein janta tha wo baat mujh par ghalib aa gaee aur maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! kya wjah hai ke falan ko nahi de rahe ? Allah ki qism ! main usey momin samajhta hun aap ne farmaya : ya musalman . iske baad mein thodi der chup raha phir jo main uskey barey mein janta tha wo baat mujh par ghalib aa gaee maine phir kaha : falan se aap ke ea'raaz ka sabab kya hai? Allah ki qism ! main to usey momin samajhta hun aap ne farmaya : ya muslimaa n. (phir) aap ne farmaya : main aik aadmi ko deta hun jabke doosra mujhey us se zyada mahboob hota hai is dar se (deta hun) ke wo aundhey munh aag mein na daal diya jaey aur Hulwani ki hadis mein) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke farmaan momin samejhtey ho ya musalman ka ( takraar do baar hai (teen baar nahi).
2434,Sufiyan-Sory-ibne-Shahab (Zohri (ke bhatijey ( Muhammad-bin-Abdullah-bin-shahaab (aur Mamar sab ne (Zohri ( se isi sanad ke sath usi (pichhli hadis) ke ham mana hadis riwayat ki.
2435,Muhammad-bin-Sad ye hadis bayan kartey hain yani Zohri ki uper zikr ki gaee hadis unhon-ne apni hadis mein kaha : to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne meri gardan aur kandhey ke darmyan apna hath maara aur farmaya : jang kar rahe ho? aey Sad ! main aik shakhs ko deta hun. padhi. ( aagey isi tarah hai jis tarah pehli riwayat mein hai).
2436,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab (Zohri ( se khabar di, kaha : mujhey Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya ke Hunain ke din jab Allah Taala ne apne rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bataur fai ( qabila ( Hawazin ko maal ata kiye aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Quraish ke logon ko so-so (100-100) oont dene shuru kiye to Ansar mein se kuchh logon ne kaha : Allah Taala Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko maaf farmaai ! aap Quraish ko de rahe hain aur hamein chhod rahe hain, halanke hamari talwaarein ( abhi tak) unke khoon ke qatrey tapkaa rahi hain. Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : unki baton mein se ye baatein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko batai gain to aap ne Ansar ko bulwa bheja aur unhein chamdey ke aik (badey) saaybaan (ke saaey ( mein jama kiya, jab wo sab ikatthey ho gaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke paas tashrif laey aur farmaya : ye kya baat hai jo mujhey tum logon ki taraf se pahunchi hai? Ansar ke samajhdaar logon ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! hamarey samajhdaar logon ne to kuchh nahi kaha, albatta ham mein se un logon ne, jo nau umr hain, ye baat kahi hai ke Allah apne rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko maaf farmaey, wo Quraish ko de rahe hain aur hamein nazar andaz kar rahe hain, halanke hamari talwaarein ( abhi tak) unke khoon ke qatrey tapkaa rahi hain. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : main unko de raha hun jo kuchh arsa qabl tak kufr par they, aisey logon ke dilon ko mutmaeen karna chahta hun, kya tum is par razi nahi ho ke log maal w daulat ley jayen aur tum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko lekar gharon ki taraf lauto? Allah ki qism ! jo kuchh tum lekar wapas ja rahe ho wo us se bahut behtar hai jisey wo log lekar lot rahe hain. to ( Ansar ( kehney lagey : kyon nahi, aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! ham ( bilkul ( razi hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : be-shak tum (apni nisbat dusron ko) bahut zyada tarjeeh miltii dekhogey to tum (us par) sabr karna yahan tak ke tum Allah aur uske rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aa milo . main hauz par hunga ( wahin mulaqat hogi. ( Ansar ne kaha : ham (har sura mein sabr ( sabr karengey."
2437,"Saleh ne ibne-Shahab (Zohri ( se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne kaha : jab Allah ne apne rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko) qabila ( Hawazin ke amwaal mein se bataur fai ata farmaya jo ata farmaya, padhi. ...aur us (pichhli hadis ke) manind (tarah) hadis bayan ki, iske siwa ke unhon ( Saleh ( ne kaha, Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ham ne sabr na kya aur unhon-ne (aur ham mein se un logon ne jo nau-umr hain ke bajaey nau-umr logon ne kaha)."
2438,"ibne-Shahab ke bhatijey ( Muhammad-bin-Abdullah ( ne apne chacha se khabar di, kaha : mujhey Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di aur isi tarah hadis bayan ki, siwaey is baat ke ke unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : un logon ( Ansar ( ne kaha : ham sabr karengey. jis tarah Yunus ne Zohri se riwayat ki."
2439,"Qatada Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan kartey hain, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ansar ko jama farmaya aur puchha : kya tum main tumharey siwa koi aur bhi hai? unhon-ne jawab diya : nahi, hamarey bhaanjey ke siwa koi aur nahi hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qaum ka bhanja unmein se hai. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Quraish thodey din qabl jahiliyat aur) gumrahi ( ki museebat mein they aur maine chaha ke unko (Islam par) pakka karun aur unki diljoii karun kya tum is par khush nahi hogey ke log duniya wapas lekar jayen aur tum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko lekar apne gharon ko lauto? agar log aik wadi mein chalein aur Ansar aik aur ghaati mein chalein to main Ansar ki ghaati mein chalun ga."
2440,"Abu-Tayyah se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne kaha : jab Makka fateh ho gaya aur) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hunain ki) ghaneematein Quraish mein taqseem kiin to Ansar ne kaha : ye badey tajjub ki baat hai, hamari talwaaron se un logon ke khoon tapak rahe hain aur hamarey amwaal ghaneemat unhi ko diye ja rahe hain ! ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tak pahunchi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unko jama kiya aur farmaya : wo kya baat hai jo tumhari taraf se mujhey pahunchi hai? unhon-ne kaha : baat wahi hai jo aap tak pahunch chuki hai wo log jhoot nahi boltey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya tum (is par) khush na hogey ke log duniya lekar apne gharon ko lautiin aur tum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko lekar apne gharon ko lauto. agar log aik wadi ya ghaati mein chalein aur Ansar dusri wadi ya ghaati mein chalein to main Ansar ki wadi ya Ansar ki ghaati mein chalun ga. (Ansar se bhi yahi tawaqqo hai.)"
2441,"Hisham-bin-Zaid-bin Anas ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : jab Hunain ki jang hui to Hawazin aur Ghatfan aur doosrey log apne biwi bachchon aur maweshiyon ko lekar aaey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath us roz das hazaar (apne sathi ( they aur wo log bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they jinhein (fatah Makka ke mauqe par ghulam banaaney ki bajaey) aazad kiya gaya tha. ye aapko chhod kar peechhey bhag gaey yahan tak ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) akeley reh gaey, kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us din ( muhajireen ke baad Ansar ko) do baar pukara, un donon ko aapas mein zarra barabar gad-mudd na kiya, aap daain taraf mutwajjeh huey aur awaz di : aey jamat Ansar ! unhon-ne kaha : labbaik , aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khush ho jayen ham aap ke sath hain. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baain taraf mutwajjeh huey aur farmaya : aey jamat Ansar ! unhon-ne kaha : labbaik , aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khush ho jaaiye , ham aap ke sath hain. aap (is waqt) safaid khachchar par Sawar they, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) nichey utrey aur farmaya : main Allah ka banda aur uska rasool hun. chunanche mushrik shikast kha gaey aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ghaneemat ke bahut se amwaal hasil kiye to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein (fatah Makka se zara qabl ( hijrat karne walon aur (fatah Makka ke mauqe par) aazad rakhey janey walon mein taqseem kar diya aur Ansar ko kuchh na diya, is par Ansar ne kaha : jab sakhti aur shiddat ka mauqa ho to hamein bulaya jata hai. aur ghaneematein dusron ko di jati hain ! ye baat Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tak pahunch gaee, is par aap ne unhein saaybaan mein jama kiya aur farmaya : aey Ansar ki jamat ! wo kya baat hai jo mujhey tumharey barey mein pahunchi hai? wo khamosh rahe, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey Ansar ki jamat ! kiya tum is baat par razi na hogey ke log duniya lekar jayen aur tum Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko apni jama'iyat mein shamil karke apne sath gharon ko ley jao . wo keh uthey : kyon nahi, aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! ham (is par) razi hain. kaha : to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar log aik wadi mein chalein aur Ansar dusri wadi mein, to main Ansar ki wadi ko ikhtiyar karunga . Hisham ne kaha maine puchha : abu-Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) ! (hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki kunniyat (aap iske (aankho dekhe) gawaah they? unhon-ne kaha : main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko chhod kar kahan ghayab ho sakta tha."
2442,"sumait ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : ham ne Makka fateh kar liya, phir ham ne Hunain mein jang ki, mere mushahidey ke mutabiq mushrik behtreen saf bandi karke ( muqaable mein) aaey. pahley ghud-sawaaron ki saf banai gaee, phir jangjuon ( ladney walon ( ki, phir iske peechhey aurton ki saf banai gaee, phir bakriyon ki qataarein khadi ki gain , phir oonton ki qataarein . kaha : aur ham ( Ansar ( bahut log they, hamari tadaad chh hazaar ko pahunch gaee thi aur hamarey pahlu ke sawaaron par Khalid-bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) they. hamarey ghud sawar hamari pushton ki taraf mudney lagey aur kuchh der na guzri thi ke hamarey sawar bikhar gaey aur baddoo bhi bhag gaey aur wo log bhi jinko ham jantey hain (Makka ke nau (new) muslim) to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne awaz di : aey muhajireen ! aey muhajireen ! phir farmaya : aey Ansar ! aey Ansar ! kaha : Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ye ( mere apne mushahidey ke ilawa jang mein Sharik logon ki) jamat ki riwayat hai, kaha : ham ne kaha : labbaik , aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aagey badhey , aur ham Allah ki qism ! un tak pahunchey bhi na they ke Allah ne unko shikast se do char kar diya, is par ham ne us sarey maal par qabza kar liya, phir ham Taaif ki taraf rawaana huey aur chalis (40) din tak unka muhaasra kiya, phir ham Makka wapas aaey aur wahan padao kiya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik aadmi ko 100 oont (ke hisab se) dene shuru kiyen,....... padhi. phir hadis ka baqi hissey isi tarah bayan kiya jis tarah ( uper ki riwayat mein) Qatada , abu Tayyah aur Hisham bin Zaid ki riwayat hai,"
2443,"Muhammad-bin-abi-Umar Makki ne kaha : Sufiyan (bin-Uena) ne hamein Umar-bin-Saeed-bin-Masruq se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid ( Saeed-bin-Masruq) se, unhon-ne abaaya-bin-rifa'a se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Rafe-bin-Khadeej (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne abu-Sufiyan-bin-harab, safwaan-bin-Umayya , Uena-bin-Hisn aur Aqra-bin-Habis (Raziallahu anhu) mein se har aik ko so-so oont diye aur Abbas-bin-mirdas (Raziallahu anhu) ko us se kam diye to Abbas bin mirdus (Raziallahu anhu) ne (ashaar mein) kaha : kya aap meri aur mere ghodey Ubaid ki ghaneemat Uena (bin-Hisn-bin-Huzaifa-bin-badr-saiyed-bin-Ghatfan) aur Aqraa (bin-haabis raees Tameem ( (Raziallahu anhu) ke darmyan qarar detey hain, halanke (Uena (Raziallahu anhu) ke pardaadaa) badr aur (aqraa' (Raziallahu anhu) ke walid) Habis kisi (badon ke) majma' main (mere walid ( se fauqiyat nahi rakhtey they aur main un donon mein se kisi se kam nahi hun aur jis ko past qarar diya jaeyga usko buland nahi kiya ja sakega. kaha : is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke bhi so poorey kar diye."
2444,Ahmad-bin-Abda zabi ne kaha : hamein ( Sufiyan ( bin-Uena ne Umar-bin-Saeed-bin-Masruq se isi sanad ke sath khabar di ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hunain ke ghanimat ka maal taqseem kiya to abu Sufiyan-bin-harab (Raziallahu anhu) ko 100 oont diye. padhi. aur pichhli hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki aur ye izafa kiya : aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Alqama-bin-Ulaasa (Raziallahu anhu) ko bhi so oont diye.
2445,"mukhlid-bin-Khalid shaeerii ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan (bin-Uena ( ne hadis sunai, kaha : mujhey Umar-bin-Saeed ne isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki aur is mein na Alqama-bin-Ulaasa (Raziallahu anhu) ka zikr kiya na safwaan-bin-Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) ka aur na apni hadis mein ashaar hi zikr kiye."
2446,"Amr-bin-Yahyaa-bin-Ammaara ne Ibad-bin-Tameem se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Hunain fateh kiya, ghanimat ka maal taqseem kiya to jinke dilon ko islam ki taraf mutmaeen karna maqsud tha unko ( bahut zyada ( ata farmaya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tak ye baat pahunchi ke Ansar bhi itna lena chahtey hain jitna doosrey logon ko mila hai to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey aur unko Khitab farmaya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Allah Taala ki hamd w sana bayan ki, phir farmaya :aey giroh Ansar ! kya maine tum ko gumrah nahi paya tha, phir Allah Taala ne mere zariey se tumhen hidayat naseeb farmai ! aur tumhen mohtaaj w zarurat mand na paya tha, phir Allah Taala ne mere zariey se tumhen ghanii kar diya ! kya tumhen muntashir na paya tha? phir Allah Taala ne mere zariey se tumhen muttahid kar diya ! un sab ne kaha : Allah aur uske rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us se bhi badh kar ehsan farmaney waley hain. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mujhey jawab nahi doge? unhon-ne kaha : Allah aur uske rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahut zyada ehsan karne waley hain. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum bhi, agar chaho to keh saktey ho aisa tha aisa tha aur mamla aisey hua, aisey hua Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bahut si baatein ginwaaein , (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamarey paas us haalat mein aaey ke aapko jhutlaayaa gaya tha, ham ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki tasdeeq ki, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko akelaa chhod diya gaya tha ham ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki madad ki, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko nikal diya gaya tha, ham ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko thikana muhaiya kiya , Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par zimme-daariyon ka bojh tha, ham ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath mawaasaat ki) Amr (bin Yahya (ka khayal hai wo unhein yad nahi rakh sakey. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kiya tum is par razi nahi hotey ke log oont aur bakriyan lekar jayen aur tum Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko apne sath lekar gharon ko jao? Ansar qareeb tar hain aur log unke baad hain ( shiaar wo kapdey jo sabse pahley jism par pahney jatey hain, Disaar wo kapdey jo baad mein odhey jatey hain) aur agar hijrat (ka farq ( na hota to main bhi Ansar ka aik fard hota aur agar log aik wadi aur ghaati mein chalein to main Ansar ki wadi aur unki ghaati mein chalun ga , bila shubah tum mere baad (khud par dusron ko) tarjeeh miltii paogey to sabr karna yahan tak ke tum mujhey hauz par aa milo."
2447,"Mansoor ne abu-Waail (Shaqeeq) se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (bin-Masood) (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : jab Hunain ki jang hui. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kuchh logon ko (maale-ghaneemat ki) taqseem mein tarjeeh di. aap ne Aqra-bin-Habis (Raziallahu anhu) ko so oont diye, Uena (Raziallahu anhu) ko bhi itney hi ( oont ( diye aur Arab ke doosrey ashraaf ko bhi ata kiya aur us din (maale-ghaneemat ki) taqseem mein na adl kiya gaya aur na Allah ki raza ko peshe-nazar rakha gaya hai. kaha : maine (dil mein) kaha : Allah ki qism ! main (is baat se) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko zaroor aagah karunga, main aap ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur is baat ki itlaa di jo usney kahi thi. (ghussey se) aap ka chehra Mubarak badal gaya. yahan tak ke wo surkh rang ki tarah ho gaya, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar Allah aur uska rasool adl nahi karengey to phir kon adl karega? ! phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Musa (Alaihissalam) par raham farmaai ! unhein is se bhi zyada azeeyat pahunchai gaee to unhon-ne sabr kiya. (ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : maine dil mein sochaa aainda kabhi (is qisam ki) koi baat aap ke samney pesh nahi karunga ."
2448,"Aamash ne ( abu-Waail ( Shaqiq se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kuchh (maal ( taqseem kiya to aik aadmi ne kaha : is taqseem mein Allah ki raza ko peshe-nazar nahi rakha gaya. kaha : main Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur chupkey-chupkey se aapko bata diya, us se aap intihai ghussey mein aa gaey, aap ka chehra surkh ho gaya. yahan tak ke maine khahish ki, kash!  ye baat main aapko na bataataa , kaha : phir aap ne farmaya : Musa (Alaihissalam) ko is se bhi zyada azeeyat pahunchai gaee to unhon-ne sabr kiya."
2449,"Leis ne Yahya-bin-Saeed se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Zubair se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hunain se waapsii ke waqt Jaarana mein aik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya jabke Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ke kapdey mein chandi thi aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us se muththii bhar-bhar ke logon ko de rahe they. to usne kaha : aey Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) adl kijiye . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : terey liye wail (halaakat ya jahannam (ho ! agar main adl nahi kar raha to kon adl karega? agar main adl nahi kar raha to main naakaam ho gaya aur khasaarey mein pad gaya. is par Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! mujhey ijazat dijiye main is munafiq ko qatl kar dun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : (main is baat se) Allah ki panah ( mangta hun) ! ke log aisi baatein karein ke main apne sathiyon ko qatl karta hun. be-shak ye aur uske sathi Quran padhengey , wo unke halaq se aagey nahi badhey ga , (ye log ( is tarah is (deen-Islam) se nikal jaeinge jis tarah teer shikar se ( aagey ( nikal jata hai."
2450,"abdul-wahaab Saqafi ne kaha : maine Yahya-bin-Saeed se suna, keh rahe they : mujhey abu-Zubair ne bataya ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, neez Qurra-bin-Khalid ne bhi abu-Zubair ke waastey se Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghaneematein taqseem farma rahe they........ padhi. aur) uper zikr ki gaee hadis ki tarah ( hadis bayan ki."
2451,"Saeed-bin-Masruq ne Abdur-Rehman bin abi-Nu-am se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) jab Yaman mein they, to unhon-ne kuchh sona Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas bheja jo apni mitti ke andar hi tha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey char afraad : Aqra-bin-Habis Hanzali, Uena (bin Hisn bin Huzaifa) bin badr fazari, Alqama-bin-Ulasa Aamiri (Raziallahu anhu) jo iske baad (aagey badey qabeeley ( banu- kilaab (bin Rabee bin Aamir (ka aik fard tha aur Zaid-al-Khair Tai (Raziallahu anhu) jo iske baad) aagey banu-Tey ki zaili shaakh (bin Nabhan ka aik fard tha, main taqseem farma diya, kaha : is par Quraish naraz ho gaey aur kehney lagey : kya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) najdi sardaron ko ata karengey aur hamein chhod dengey ? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye kaam maine unki talife-qalb ki khaatir kya hai. itney mein ghani dadhi , ubhrey huey rukhsaaron, dhansi hui aankhon, nikli hui peshani , mundey huey sar wala aik shakhs aaya aur kaha : aey Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! Allah se darein ! to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar main uski nafarmani karunga to uski farmanbardari kon karega ! wo to mujhey tamam poori zamin ke logon par ameen samajhta hai aur tum mujhey ameen nahi samajhtey? phir wo aadmi peeth pher kar chal diya, logon mein se aik shakhs ne usko qatl karne ki ijazat talab ki. bayan karne waley samajhtey hain ke wo Khalid-bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) they. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : uski asl (jis qabeeley se iska apna talluq hai) se aisi qaum hogi jo Quran padhegi lekin wo unke galey se nichey nahi utarega. wo ahale-Islam ko qatl karengey aur but paraston ko chhod dengey. wo Islam se is tarah nikal jaeinge jis tarah teer nishana banaey janey waley shikar se nikal jata hai, agar maine unko pa liya to main har sura unhein is tarah qatl karunga jis tarah (azab bhej kar) qaume-aad ko qatl kya gaya."
2452,"abdul-Wahid ne Ammara-bin-Qaqa se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Abdur-Rehman bin abi-Nu-am ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ko farmatey huey suna ke Hazrat Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ne Yaman se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein rangey huey ( dabaaghat shuda ( chamdey mein (kachchey) soney ka aik tukda bheja jisey mitti se alag nahi kya gaya tha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey char afraad : Uena bin Hisn , Aqra-bin-Habis , Zaid al-Khail aur chauthey fard Alqama-bin-Ulaasa ya Aamir-bin-Tufail (Raziallahu anhu) ke darmyan taqseem kar diya. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sathiyon mein se aik aadmi ne kaha : ham is ( atiye (ke un logon ki nisbat zyada haq daar they. kaha : ye baat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tak pahunchi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya tum mujhey ameen nahi samajhtey? halanke main uska ameen hun jo aasman mein hai, mere paas subah w Sham aasman ki khabar aati hai. ( Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : ghani dadhi, ubhrey huey rukhsaron , dhansi hui aankhon , nikli hui peshani , mundey huey sar wala aur pindli tak uthey tehband wala aik shakhs khada hua, usne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! Allah se dariye . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tujh par afsos , kya main tamam ahale-zameen se badh kar Allah se darney ka haqdar nahi hun ! phir wo aadmi peeth pher kar chal diya. to Khalid-bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kya main iski gardan na uda dun? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : nahi, ho sakta hai ke wo Namaz padhta ho. Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : kitney hi namazi hain jo zaban se (wo baat ( kehtey hain ( kalima padhtey hain) jo unke dilon mein nahi. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mujhey ye hukm nahi diya gaya ke logon ke dilon mein suraakh karun aur na ye ke unke pet chaak karun. phir jab wo pusht pher kar ja raha tha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uski taraf dekha aur farmaya : ye haqiqat hai ke uski asl se aisey log niklengey jo Allah ki kitab ko badi taraawat se padhengey ( lekin) wo unke galey se nichey nahi utregi, wo Deen se is tarah nikal jaeinge jaisey teer nishana banaey janey waley shikar se nikalta hai. ( Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : mera khayal hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar maine unko pa liya to unhein is tarah qatl karunga jis tarah Samood qatl huey they."
2453,"Jarir ne Ammara-bin-Qaqa se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Alqama-bin-Ulaasa (Raziallahu anhu) ka zikr kya aur Aamir-bin-Tufail (Raziallahu anhu) ka zikr nahi kya. phir ( nikli hui peshani wala ( kaha aur) abdul-Wahid ki tarah ( naashiz ( (Ubhri hui peshani wala ( nahi kaha aur un alfaz ka izafa kya ke umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) uth kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaey aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! kya main uski gardan na uda dun? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : nahi. kaha : phir wo peeth pher kar chal padaa to Khalid Saifullah (Raziallahu anhu) uth kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas hazir huey aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kya main uski gardan na uda dun? to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : nahi. phir farmaya : haqiqat ye hai ke bahut jald uski asl se aisey log niklengey jo Allah Taala ki kitab narmi aur taraawat se padhengey. ( Jarir ne) kaha : Umara ne kaha : mera khayal hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar maine unko pa liya to unko isi tarah qatl karunga jis tarah Samood qatl huey."
2454,"Ammara-bin-Qaqa ke aik doosrey shagird ibne- Fuzel ne isi sanad ke sath ye hadis bayan ki aur kaha : ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kachcha sona ( char afraad : Zaid al-Khail , Aqra-bin-Habis , Uena bin Hisn aur Alqama-bin-Ulaasa ya Aamir-bin-Tufail (Raziallahu anhu) main ( taqseem kya. (aur abdul-Wahid ki riwayat ki tarah ubhri hui peshani wala kaha aur unhon-ne uski asl se (jis se iska talluq hai) aik qaum nikley gii ke alfaz bayan kiye aur ( لَئِنْ أَدْرَكْتُهُمْ لَأَقْتُلَنَّهُمْ قَتْلَ ثَمُودَ) (agar maine unko pa liya to unko is tarah qatl karunga jis tarah Samood qatl huey) ke alfaz zikr nahi kiye."
2455,"Muhammad-bin Ibrahim ne abu-Salma aur Ata-bin-Yasar se riwayat ki ke wo donon Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur unse Haruriya ke barey mein malum kya : kya aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko unka tazkira kartey huey suna tha? unhon-ne kaha : Haruriya ko to main nahi janta, albatta maine ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey ye suna hai : is ummat mein aik qaum niklegi. aap ne is ummat mein se nahi kaha, tum apni namazon ko unki namazon se kamtar samjhogey, wo Quran padhengey aur wo unke halaq . ya unke galey . se nichey nahi utrega . wo is tarah Deen se nikal jaeinge jis tarah teer shikar kiye huey janwar se nikal jata hai aur teer andaz apne teer ki lakdi ko , uske phal ko , uski taant ko dekhta hai aur uske pichhley hissey ( so faar ya chutki) ke barey mein shak mein mubtala hota hai ke kaha iske sath ( shikar ke) khoon mein kuchh laga hai. ( teer tezi se nikal jaey to is par khoon wghaira zyada nahi lagta . isi tarah tezi ke sath Deen se nikalney waley par Deen ka koi asar baqi nahi rehta .)"
2456,"ibne-Shahab se riwayat hai, kaha : mujhey abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman aur Zuhhaak Hamdani ne khabar di ke Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir they aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kuchh maal taqseem farma rahe they ke usi beech mein aap ke paas ( zul-khuwesra ( jo banu- Tameem ka aik fard tha, aaya aur kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! adl kijiye . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : teri halaakat (ka saman ho ( ! agar main adl nahi karunga to kon adl karega? agar main adl nahi kar raha to main naakaam ho gaya aur khasaarey mein pad gaya. (ya agar maine adl na kya to tum naakaam rahogey aur khasaarey mein hogey ( is par Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! mujhey ijazat dijiye main is munafiq ko qatl kar dun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : usey chhod do, iske kuchh sathi hongey. tumhara koi fard apni Namaz ko unki Namaz aur apne rozon ko unke rozon ke samney heech samjheyga, ye log Quran padhengey lekin unki hansliyon se nichey nahi utrega. Islam se is tarah niklengey jaisey teer nishana banaey gaey shikar se nikalta hai. uske phal (ya paikan ( ko dekha jaey to usmein kuchh nahi paya jata, phir iske so faar ko dekha jaey to usmein bhi kuchh nahi paya jata, phir uske par ko dekha jaey to usmein kuchh nahi paya jata, wo ( teer ( gobar aur khoon se aagey nikal gaya ( lekin is par laga kuchh bhi nahi ( , unki nishani aik siyah faam mard hai, iske donon moondhon mein se aik moondha aurat ke pistaan ki tarah ya gosht ke hiltey huey tukdey ki tarah hoga. wo logon ( musalmanon (ke aapsi ikhtilaf ke waqt ( namudaar ( hongey. Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main gawahi deta hun ke maine ye hadis Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni hai aur main gawahi deta hun ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne unke khilaf jang ki, mein unke sath tha. unhon-ne us aadmi (ko talash karne) ke barey mein hukm diya, usey talash kya gaya to wo mil gaya, us (ki laash ( ko laya gaya to maine usko isi tarah dekha jis tarah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uska Taaruf : karaya tha."
2457,"Sulaiman ne abu-Nazara se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kuchh logon ka tazkira farmaya jo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ummat mein hongey, wo logon mein iftiraaq ke waqt se niklengey , unki nishani sar mundana hogi, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wo makhlooq ke badtareen log . ya makhlooq ke badtareen logon mein se hongey, unko 2 girohon mein se wo ( giroh ( qatl karega jo haq ke qareeb tar hoga. aap ne unki misal bayan ki ya baat irshad farmai : insan shikar ko . ya farmaya : nishaney ko teer maarta hai wo phal ko dekhta hai to usey ( khoon ka ( nishan nazar nahi aata (jis se baseerat hasil ho jaey ke shikar ko laga hai), paikan aur par ke darmyani hissey ko dekhta hai to koi nishan nazar nahi aata , wo sofaar ( pichhley hissey ( ko dekhta hai to koi nishan nahi dekhta . Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aey Iraq walo! tum hi ne unko (Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki maiyat (sath) mein) qatl kya hai."
2458,"Qasim bin Fazal Hadani ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : ham se abu-Nazara ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : musalmanon mein iftiraq ke waqt tezi se (apne hadaf ke andar se) nikal janey wala aik giroh niklega 2 jamaton mein se jo jamat haq se zyada talluq rakhney wali hogi, ( wahi ( usey qatl karegi ."
2459,"Qatada ne abu-Nazara se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : meri ummat ke 2 giroh hongey un donon ke darmyan se, Deen mein se tezi se bahar ho janey waley niklengey , unhein wo giroh qatl karega jo donon girohon mein se zyada haq ke laaiq hoga."
2460,Dawud ne abu-Nazara se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : logon mein giroh bandi ke waqt Deen mein se tezi se nikal janey wala aik firqa tezi se niklega . unke qatl ki zimme-dari donon jamaton mein se haq se zyada talluq rakhney wali jamat poori karegi .
2461,"Suhak mashriqi ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye baat aik hadis mein riwayat ki jis mein aap ne us qaum ka tazkira farmaya jo ( ummat ke) mukhtalif girohon mein batney ke waqt nikleygi, unko donon girohon mein se haq se qareeb tar giroh qatl karega ."
2462,"Wakee ne hadis bayan ki, kaha Aamash ne hamein khaisma se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Suwed bin Ghafala se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya jab main tumhen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hadis sunaun to ye baat ke main aasman se gir padun mujhey is se zyada pasand hai ke main aap ki taraf koi aisi baat mansub karun jo aap ne nahi farmai aur jab main tum se us mamley mein baat karun jo mere aur tumharey darmyan hai (to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke us qaul se istishhad kar sakta hun ke) jang aik chaal hai) lekin) maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko (sarahat ke sath) farmatey huey suna : an-qareeb ( khilafate-rashida ke) aakhiri zamaney mein aik qaum niklegi wo log kam Umr aur kam aql hongey ( bazahir ( makhlooq ki sabse behtreen baat kahengey Quran padhengey jo unke halaq se nichey nahi utrega Deen ke andar se is tarah tezi se nikal jaeinge jis tarah teer tezi se shikar ke andar se nikal jata hai jab tumhara unse saamna ho to unko qatl kar dena jisne unko qatl kya uske liye yaqinan qiyamat ke din Allah ke yahan ajr hai."
2463,Esa-bin-Yonus aur Sufiyan donon ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
2464,Aamash se Jarir aur abu-Muawiya ne isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki aur un donon ki hadis mein Deen mein se tez raftari ke sath yun niklengey jis tarah teer nishana lagey shikar se tezi se nikal jata hai ke alfaz nahi hain.
2465,"Ayub ne Muhammad se unhon-ne Ubeda se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne khawarij ka zikr kya aur kaha : unmein aik aadmi naaqis , chhotey ya zyada aur hiltey huey gosht ke) jaisey ( hath wala hoga agar tumharey itraaney ka dar na hota to jo kuchh Allah Taala ne unhein qatl karne walon ke liye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zaban se wada farmaya hai wo main tumhen batata. (Ubaida ne) kaha maine kaha : kya aap ne ye (wada seedhey-seedhey ( Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai? unhon-ne kaha : rabe-Kaba ki qism ! haan , rab Kaba ki qism ! haan , rab Kaba ki qism ! haan"
2466,"Ibne-Aun ne Muhammad se aur unhon-ne Ubeda se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha, main tumhen sirf wahi bayan karunga jo maine un ( Ali (Raziallahu anhu)) se suna hai phir unhon-ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se Ayub ki hadis ki tarah marfu hadis bayan ki."
2467,"Salma bin kuheil ne kaha : mujhey Zaid-bin Wahab Johni (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis sunai ke wo us lashkar mein shamil they jo Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath tha (aur ( khawarij ki taraf rawana hua tha to Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : logo ! maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : meri ummat se kuchh log niklengey wo (is tarah) Quran padhengey ke tumhari qirat unki qirat ke muqabley mein kuchh na hogi aur na tumhari namazon ki unki namazon ke muqabley mein koi haisiyat hogi aur na hi tumharey rozon ki unke rozon ke muqabley mein koi haisiyat hogi. wo Quran padhengey aur khayal karengey wo unke haq mein hai halanke wo unke khilaf hoga unki Namaz unki hansliyon se aagey nahi badhegi wo is tarah tez raftari ke sath Islam se nikal jaeinge jis tarah teer bahut tezi se shikar ke andar se nikal jata hai. agar wo lashkar jo unko ja lega jaan ley ke unke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zaban se unke barey mein kya faisla hua hai to wo amal se (be niyaaz ho kar sirf usi amal par) bharosa kar lein. us ( giroh ( ki nishani ye hai ke unmein aik aadmi hoga jiska azad ( bazu, kandhey se lekar kohni tak ka hissa ( hoga kalaai nahi hogi iske bazu ke sirey par pistaan ki nok ki tarah (ka nishan) hoga jis par safaid baal hongey to log Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) aur ahale-Sham (Syria) ki taraf ja rahe ho aur un ( logon ( ko chhod rahe ho jo tumharey baad tumharey bachchon aur amwal par aa padengey Allah ki qism ! mujhey ummeed hai ke ye wahi qaum hai kyonke unhon-ne ( musalmanon ka ( hurmat wala khoon bahaya hai aur logon ke maweshiyon par ghaarat gari ki hai Allah ka naam lekar (unki taraf ( chalo. Salma bin kuheil ne kaha : mujhey Zaid-bin Wahab ne (eik aik ( manzil mein utara (har manzil ke barey mein tafseel se) bataya yahan tak ke bataya : ham aik pul par se guzrey phir jab hamara aamna-samna hua to us roz khawarij ka sipeh salaar Abdullah-bin Wahab Rasbi tha us ne unse kaha : apne neze phenk 2 aur apni talwaarein niyaamon se nikal lo kyonke mujhey khatrah hai ke wo tumharey samney (Suleh ke liye Allah ka naam ( pukaarengey jis tarah unhon-ne haroora ke din tumharey samney pukara tha to unhon-ne lot kar apne neze door phenk diye aur talwaarein soont lin to log unhi nezon ke sath un par pul padey aur wo aik doosrey par qatl huey (eik ke baad doosra aata aur qatl ho kar pahluon par girta) aur us roz ( Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ka sath dene waale) logon mein se do ke siwa koi aur qatl na hua Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha unmein adhoorey hath waley ko talash karo logon ne bahut dhoonda lekin usko na pa sakey is par Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) khud uthey aur un logon ke paas aaey jo qatl ho kar aik doosrey par girey huey they aap ne farmaya : unko hatao to unhon-ne usey ( laashon ke nichey ( zamin se laga hua paya. aap ne Allahu-akbar kaha phir kaha : Allah ne sach farmaya aur uske Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (usi tarah ham tak) pahuncha diya. ( Zaid-bin Wahab ne) kaha Ubeda salmaanii khadey ho kar aap ke samney hazir huey aur kaha aey ameerul-momeneen ! us Allah ki qism jiske siwa koi ibadat ke laaiq nahi ! aap ne waqei ye hadis Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni thi? to unhon-ne kaha : haan us Allah ki qism jiske siwa koi ibadat ke laaiq nahi ! yahan tak ke usne aap se teen baar qism li aur aap iske samney Halaf uthatey rahe."
2468,abu-Taahir aur Yunus bin abdul-Aala donon ne kaha hamein Abdullah-bin Wahab ne khabar di unhon-ne kaha mujhey Amr-bin-Haris ne Bukair ashajj se khabar di unhon-ne Basar-bin-Saeed se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aazad karda ghulam Hazrat abu Raafe (Raziallahu anhu) ke betey Ubaidullah se riwayat ki ke jab harooriya ne khurooj kya aur wo ( Ubaidullah (Hazrat Ali-bin abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath tha to unhon-ne kaha hukumat Allah ke siwa kisi ki nahi Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ye kalima haq hai jis se baatil murad liya gaya hai Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kuchh logon ki sifaat bayan kin mein un logon mein un sifaat ko khub pehchanta hun (aap ne farmaya ( : wo apni zabanon se haq baat kahengey aur wo ( haq ( unki us jagah. aap ne apne halaq ki taraf ishara kya. se aagey nahi badhey ga ye Allah Taala ki makhlooq mein se iske haan sabse zyada na-pasandida hain unmein aik siyah rang ka aadmi hoga iska aik hath bakri ke than ya noke-pistan ki tarah hoga. jab Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne unko qatl kya to kaha : dhundo . logon ne dhunda to unhein kuchh na mila farmaya dobara talash karo Allah ki qism ! maine jhoot nahi bola aur na mujhey jhoot bataya gaya 2 ya teen baar ( yahi fiqra ( kaha phir unhon-ne usey aik khandar mein pa liya to wo usey ley aaey yahan tak ke usey aap ke samney rakh diya. Ubaidullah ne kaha : main bhi unke us mamley main aur unke mutaalliq Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki baat ke waqt hazir tha. yo nas ne apni riwayat mein izafa kya : Bukair ne kaha mujhey ( Abdullah (bin Hunain ( hashmi) se aik aadmi ne hadis bayan ki usne kaha maine bhi us kaley ko dekha tha.
2469,"Abdullah-bin-Samit ne Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya bila shubah mere baad meri ummat se. . padhi. ya an-qareeb mere baad meri ummat se. . padhi. aik qaum hogi jo Quran padhengey wo unke gallon se nichey nahi utrey ga wo Deen se is tarah nikal jaeinge jaisey teer shikar se nikal jata hai phir usmein wapas nahi aaeingey. wo insanon aur makhlooqat mein bad-tareen hongey. ibne- Samit ne kaha : main hukm ghafaari (Raziallahu anhu) ko mila, maine kaha : (ye ( kya hadis hai jo maine Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se is tarah suni hai? iske baad maine ye hadis bayan ki to unhon-ne kaha maine bhi ye hadis Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni hai."
2470,Ali-bin-Mus-hir ne ( Abu-Ishaq Shebani se aur unhon-ne yaseer-bin-Amr se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha maine Sahal-bin-Haneef (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha kya aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khawaarij ka tazkira kartey huey sunaa? unhon-ne kaha maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye suna tha. padhi. aur aap ne apne hath se mashriq ki taraf ishara kiya tha. padhi. aik qaum hogi jo apni zabanon se Quran Majeed ki tilawat karengey lekin wo unki hanslii ki haddiyon se aagey nahi jaeyga wo Deen se is tarah tezi se nikal jaeinge jis tarah teer shikar mein se nikal jata hai.
2471,abdul-Wahid ne kaha : hamein ( Abu-Ishaq ( Sulaiman Shebani ne isi sanad ke sath (mazkura (uper zikr) ( hadis bayan ki aur kaha us ( taraf ( se kuchh qaumein niklin gii .
2472,awaam-bin-Haishab se riwayat hai kaha Abu-Ishaq Shebani ne Sahal-bin-Haneef (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki farmaya : aik qaum mashriq ki taraf sargardaan phirey gii unke sar mundhey huey hongey.
2473,"Ubaidullah-bin-Muaz Anbari ne kaha : hamein mere walid ne hadis bayan ki unhon-ne kaha hamein Shoba ne Muhammad-bin-Ziyad se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko bayan kartey huey suna ke Hazrat Hasan-bin-Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne sadqey ki khajooron mein se aik khajoor ley li aur usey apne munh mein daal liya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : chhodo , chhodo , phenk do usey. kya tum nahi jantey ke ham sadqa nahi khaatey?"
2474,Wakee ne Shoba se usi ( uper zikr ki gaee (sanad ke sath riwayat ki aur) ham sadqa nahi khaatey ke bajaey) hamarey liye sadqa halal nahi kaha hai.
2475,Muhammad-bin-Jafar aur ibne-abi-Adi donon ne Shoba se isi sanad ke sath (usi tarah) hadis bayan ki jis tarah ibne- Muaz ne kaha : ke ham sadqa nahi khaatey .
2476,"Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ke aazad karda ghulam abu Yunus ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : main apne ghar laut'taa hon aur apne bistar par aik khajoor giri hui paata hon. main usey khaney ke liye uthata hon phir darta hun ke ye sadqa na ho to usey phenk deta hun."
2477,Hammam-bin-Munabbah ne kaha : ye ( hadisen ( hain jo Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein Muhammad rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kiin unhon-ne kuchh hadisein bayan kiin unmein se (eik hadis ye ( hai aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah ki qism ! main apne ghar walon ke paas laut'taa hon aur apne bistar par. padhi. ya apne ghar mein. padhi. aik khajoor giri hui paata hon main usey khaney ke liye uthata hon phir main darta hun ke kahin ye sadqa ( na (ho (ya sadqey mein se na ho ( to main usey phenk deta hun.
2478,Sufiyan ne Mansoor se unhon-ne Talha-bin-musrif se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aik khajoor mili to aap ne farmaya : agar ye ( imkan ( na hota ke ye sadqey mein se ho sakti hai to main usey kha leta.
2479,Zayda ne Mansoor aur unhon-ne Talha-bin-musarrif se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) rastey mein) padi hui ( aik khajoor ke qareeb se guzrey to farmaya : agar ye ( imkan ( na hota ke ye sadqey se hogi to main isey kha leta.
2480,Qatada ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aik khajoor mili to aap ne farmaya : agar ye ( imkan ( na hota ke ye sadqa hoga to main usey kha leta.
2481,"Imam Malik ne Zohri se riwayat ki ke Abdullah-bin-naufal-bin-Haaris-bin-abdul-Muttalib ne unhein hadis bayan ki ke abdul-Muttalib-bin-Rabee-bin-Haaris (bin-abdul-Muttalib ( (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha Rabee-bin-Haaris aur Abbas-bin-abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) ikatthey huey aur donon ne kaha : Allah ki qism ! agar ham in donon ladkon ko , unhon-ne (ye baat ( mere aur Fazal-bin-Abbaas (Raziallahu anhu) ke barey mein kahi . padhi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein bhejiin aur ye donon aap se baat karein aur aap in donon ko un sadqaat ki wsoolii par muqarrar kar dein jo kuchh (doosrey ( log ( la kar) ada kartey hain. ye donon ada karein aur in donon ko bhi wahi kuchh miley jo (doosrey) logon ko milta hai (to kitna achchha ho !). wo donon isi (mashwarey) mein (mashghool ( they ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) aaey aur unke paas khadey ho gaey in donon ne is baat ka unke samney zikr kiya to Hazrat Ali-bin-abi-Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aap donon aisa na karein Allah ki qism ! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ye kaam karne waley nahi is par Rabee-bin-Haaris (Raziallahu anhu) unke dar-pai ho gaey aur kaha Allah ki qism ! tum mahz isliye hamarey sath aisa kar rahe ho, take tum ham par apni bartarii jataao. Allah ki qism ! tumhen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke daamaad honey ka sharf hasil hua to (is mauqe par) ham ne to tum par bartarii nahi jataaii thi. Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha tum un donon ko bhej do. wo donon chaley gaey aur Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu)) wahin ( let gaey ( ibne- Rabee (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zohar ki Namaz padha li to wo donon aap se pahley hujrey ke qareeb pahunch gaey aur kaha : ham wahan khadey ho gaey yahan tak ke jab aap tashrif laey to ( izhar apnaaiyat ke taur par) hamarey kaan pakad liye phir farmaya : tum donon ke dil mein jo kuchh hai usey nikaalo ( iska izhar karo). phir aap andar dakhil huey ham bhi sath hi dakhil ho gaey us din aap Zainab-binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan they. ham ne guftgu aik doosrey par dali (har aik ne chaha doosra baat karey) phir ham mein se aik ne guftgu shuru ki kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! aap sab logon se badh kar ehsan karne waley aur sab logon se zyada sila rehmii karne waley hain. ham donon nikah ki umr ko pahunch gaey hain ham isliye hazir huey hain ke aap hamein bhi un sadqaat mein se kuchh ( sadqaat ( ki wsoolii ke liye muqarrar farma dein jis tarah log la kar ada kartey hain ham bhi la kar dengey aur jis tarah unhein milta hai hamein bhi milega. aap khasi der tak khamosh rahe yahan tak ke ham ne dobara guftgu karne ka irada kar liya. kaha to Hazrat Zenab (Raziallahu anha) pardey ke peechhey se ishara karne lageiin ke tum donon un ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) se baat na karo. kaha : phir ( kuchh der baad) aap ne farmaya : aale Muhammad ke liye sadqa munasib nahi. ye to logon (ke maal (ka mail kuchal hai. ( mahmiya ( wo khums (ghaneemat ke paanchwein hissey) par maamoor they.... ۔  aur naufal-bin-Haaris-bin-abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) ko mere paas bulao . kaha wo donon aap ki khidmat mein hazir huey to aap ne mahmiya (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : is ladkey ( Fazal-bin-Abbaas (Raziallahu anhu)) se apni beti ka nikah kar do. to usne unka nikah kar diya aur aap ne naufal-bin-Haaris (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha tum is ladkey se apni beti ki shadi kar do. mere barey mein. to usne mera nikah kar diya aur aap ne mahmiya (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : khums (jo Allah aur uske Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye tha) mein se un donon ka itna-itna haq mehar ada kar do. Zohri ne kaha us ( Abdullah-bin-Abdullah ( ne haq mehar mujhey nahi bataya."
2482,"Younus-bin-Yazeed ne ibne-Shahab se aur unhon-ne Abdullaah-bin-Haaris-bin-naufal haashmii se riwayat ki ke Hazrat abdul-Muttalib-bin-Rabee-bin-Haaris-bin-abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bataya ke unke walid Rabee-bin-Haaris-bin-abdul-Muttalib aur Abbas-bin-abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) ne abdul-Muttalib-bin-Rabee aur Fazal-bin-Abbaas (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha tum donon Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas jao . padhi. aur Imam Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ki) uper zikr ki gaee ( hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki aur is mein kaha Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne apni chadar bichhaaii aur is par let gaey aur kaha, main baat par dat janey wala abu-Hasan hon. Allah ki qism ! main apni jagah nahi chhodunga yahan tak ke tum donon ke betey jis maqsad ke liye unhein bhej rahe ho uska jawab lekar tumharey paas wapas ( na ( aa jaaein. aur us hadis mein kaha : phir aap ne hamein farmaya : ye sadqaat logon ka mail kuchail hain aur yaqinan ye Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur aale Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke liye halal nahi aur ye bhi kaha : phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya mere paas ( mahmiya-bin-juz ( (Raziallahu anhu) ko bulao . wo banu-Asad ka aik fard tha jisey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne amwaal khums ke intizaamaat ke liye muqarrar kiya tha."
2483,Leis ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki ke Ubaid-bin-sabaaq ne kaha Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bevi Hazrat Juweriya ( binte-Haaris ( (Raziallahu anhu) ne unko bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke yahaan tashrif laey aur puchha : kya khaney ki koi cheez hai? unhon-ne kaha nahi Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam). Allah ki qism ! hamarey paas us bakri ki haddi ( waley gosht (ke siwa khaney ki aur koi cheez nahi jo meri aazad karda londi ko bataur sadqa di gaee thi. aap ne farmaya : usey hi ley aao wo apne maqam par pahunch chuki hai. (jis ko sadqe ke taur par di gaee thi usey mil gaee hai aur uski milkiyat mein aa chuki hai)
2484,ibne-Uena ne Zohri se isi sanad ke sath usi (mazkura (uper zikr) hadis) ki tarah riwayat bayan ki.
2485,Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai unhon-ne kaha (Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki aazad karda kaneez (Hazrat Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ne kuchh gosht jo is par sadqa kiya gaya tha. Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bataur hadiya pesh kiya to aap ne farmaya : wo uske liye sadqa aur hamarey liye hadiya hai.
2486,Aswad ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko gaaey ka gosht pesh kiya gaya aur bataya gaya ke ye Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ko bataur sadqa diya gaya tha to aap ne farmaya : wo uske liye sadqa aur hamaare liye hadiya hai.
2487,"Hisham-bin-Urwa ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-Qasim se, unhon-ne apne walid (Qasim-bin-Muhammad -bin-abi-Bakr) se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ke hawale se teen (sharaee) faisley huey they. log usko sadqa detey they aur wo hamein tohfa de deti thin. maine iska tazkira Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kiya to aap ne farmaya : wo is par sadqa hai aur tumharey liye hadiya hai to tum usey (bila hichkichaahat) khaao."
2488,"Samak aur Shoba ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-Qasim se riwayat ki kaha maine Qasim se suna, wo Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke hawale se Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us (pichhli hadis) ki tarah bayan kar rahe they."
2489,Rabee ne Qasim se unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki albatta unhon-ne (is hadis mein) kaha : wo uski taraf se hamarey liye hadiya hai.
2490,Hazrat umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey sadqey ki aik bakri bheji maine usmein se kuchh Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki taraf bhej diya. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan tashrif laey to aap ne puchha : kya aap ke paas ( khaney ke liye) kuchh hai? unhon-ne kaha : nahi albatta (nasiiba) ( umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu)) ne us ( sadqey ki) bakri mein se kuchh hissey bheja hai jo aap ne unke yahaan bheji thi aap ne farmaya : wo apni jagah pahunch chuki hai.
2491,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko jab khana pesh kiya jata aap iske barey mein poochhtey agar ye kaha jata ke tohfa hai to usey kha letey aur agar kaha jata ke sadqa hai to usey na khaatey.
2492,Wakee aur Muaz Anbari ne Shoba se aur unhon-ne Amr-bin-Murra se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha Hazrat Abdullah-bin-abi-Ufa (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein hadis bayan ki unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas jab log ( baitul-maal mein adaaeygi ke liye) apna sadqa latey aap farmatey aey Allah ! un par  rehmat farma ! mere walid abu-oofaa (Raziallahu anhu) bhi aap ke paas apna sadqa laey to aap ne farmaya : aey Allah ! abu oofaa ki aal par rehmat nazil farmaa.
2493,Abdullah-bin-Idris ne Shoba se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki albatta unhon-ne (abi ooufaa ki aal) ke bajaey) ''un sab par rehmat bhej'' kaha.
2494,Hazrat Jareer-bin-Abdullaah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai unhon-ne kaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tumharey paas sadqa wsool karne wala aaey to wo tumharey yahaan se us haal mein lotey ke wo tum se khush ho.
